20public%20service%20content%2C%20including%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%20This%20statement%20came%20in%20response%20to%20allegations%20that%20it%20had%20sent%20copyright%20infringement%20notices%20to%20YouTubers%20regarding%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGurdeep%20Singh%20Sappal%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20executive%20officer%2Feditor%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20TV%2C%20raised%20the%20issue%20and%20argued%20that%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20are%20national%20assets%20of%20historical%20value%20and%20should%20be%20freely%20accessible%2C%20not%20subject%20to%20copyright.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrasar%20Bharti%20has%20sent%20notices%20to%20YouTubers%20invoking%20copyright%20on%20it.%20This%20is%20wrong.%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%20are%20national%20assets%20of%20historical%20value.%20They%20are%20not%20a%20commercial%20product%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20profiteering%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20copyright.%20In%20fact%2C%20any%20attempt%20to%20limit%20the%20access%20to%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20amounts%20to%20censorship%20and%20is%20an%20infringement%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20citizens%20(to)%20be%20informed%20of%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sappal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20part%20of%20parliamentary%20debate%20can%20only%20be%20restricted%20from%20public%20access%20by%20a%20specific%20order%20of%20the%20Chair%20only%2C%20using%20the%20powers%20vested%20in%20them%20to%20expunge%20parts%20of%20proceedings.%20When%20I%20had%20started%20RSTV%2C%20this%20issue%20was%20deliberated%20upon%20by%20the%20Content%20Advisory%20Committee%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20It%20was%20the%20unanimous%20decision%20that%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20have%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20anyone%20free%20of%20cost%2C%20to%20be%20used%20freely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Prasar%20Bharati%20officials%20emphasised%20that%20they%20had%20never%20issued%20such%20copyright%20notices%2C%20and%20their%20public%20service-related%20content%20is%20copyright-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprasar-bharati-does-not-make-copyright-claims-on-public-service-content-say-officials%2Farticle67369734.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20sometimes%20copyright%20violation%20notices%20might%20be%20automatically%20generated%20due%20to%20platform%20algorithms%2C%20but%20they%20encourage%20affected%20individuals%20to%20contest%20such%20notices%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20this%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20released%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20report%2C%20Sappal%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20statement%20attributed%20to%20Prasar%20Bharti%20officials%20would%20have%20been%20a%20welcome%20one%2C%20if%20only%20it%20were%20an%20official%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20intent%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti%20is%20indeed%20not%20to%20claim%20copyright%20over%20the%20usage%20of%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20then%20it%20must%20issue%20an%20official%20statement%20clarifying%20it.%20Such%20a%20statement%20can%20then%20be%20used%20by%20social%20media%20content%20creators%20for%20their%20official%20reply%20to%20the%20notices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20statement%20attributed%20to%20Prasar%20Bharti%20officials%20would%20have%20been%20a%20welcome%20one%2C%20if%20only%20it%20were%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20intent%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti%20is%20indeed%20not%20to%20claim%20copyright%20over%20the%20usage%20of%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20then%20it%20must%20issue%20an%20official%20statement%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ftuz2sGYxvs%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ftuz2sGYxvs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbU3xgYPHFX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbU3xgYPHFX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gurdeep%20Singh%20Sappal%20(%40gurdeepsappal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgurdeepsappal%2Fstatus%2F1708671318785450363%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696236603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F10%2Fprasar-bharati-hq.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fprasar-bharati-does-not-make-copyright-claims-on-public-service-content-say-officials%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20this%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20released%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fprasar-bharati-does-not-make-copyright-claims-on-public-service-content-say-officials%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20Protest%20in%20Delhi%20Demanding%20Restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02141625%2FF7WJ7MBbgAAs4cz.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thousands%20of%20government%20employees%20gathered%20at%20the%20Ram%20Lila%20Maidan%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20protest%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20and%20demand%20full%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20on%20Sunday%20(October%201).%20The%20protestors%20comprised%20Central%20and%20state%20government%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20units%20of%20over%2020%20states.%20Termed%20the%20%E2%80%9CPension%20Shanknaad%20Rally%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20protest%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20National%20Movement%20for%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NMOPS)%2C%20as%20association%20steering%20the%20campaign%20for%20restoration%20of%20the%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20PTI%2C%20NMOPS%20leader%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Bandhu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20spreading%20the%20message%20for%20OPS%20restoration%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20old%20pension%20has%20been%20restored%20in%20four%20or%20five%20states%20through%20our%20efforts%20and%20struggle.%20Our%20team%20believes%20that%20if%20the%20central%20government%20ratifies%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%20then%20the%20onus%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20on%20the%20state%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20employees%20who%20joined%20government%20service%20after%20January%201%2C%202004%2C%20are%20strongly%20opposing%20the%20New%20Pension%20Scheme.%20The%20employees%20are%20worried%20about%20their%20future%20after%20retirement%20because%20they%20are%20being%20forced%20into%20the%20NPS%20and%20deprived%20of%20the%20OPS%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shiv%20Gopal%20Mishra%2C%20national%20convener%20and%20general%20secretary%20of%20All%20India%20Railway%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Federation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2023%2F10%2F01%2Fmassive-protest-rally-delhi-govt-employees-against-new-pension-scheme.html%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EManorama%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20NPS%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20government%20employees%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20it.%20While%20OPS%20factored%20in%20inflation%20and%20pension%20payouts%20based%20on%20pay%20commission%20indices%20without%20any%20contribution%20from%20the%20employee%2C%20the%20NPS%20is%20decided%20by%20the%20contribution%20of%20both%20the%20employee%20and%20the%20employer%20and%20the%20returns%20are%20market-based%20instead%20of%20a%20fixed%20sum%20based%20on%20the%20salary%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fopposition-ex-military-personnel-new-disability-pension-rules-slam%5C%22%3EOpposition%2C%20Ex-Military%20Personnel%20Slam%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20New%20Disability%20Pension%20Rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20argued%20that%20the%20NPS%20will%20put%20much%20lesser%20burden%20on%20the%20government%20exchequer%20than%20the%20OPS%2C%20and%20the%20probability%20of%20higher%20returns%20is%20high.%20However%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20government%20employees%20opposed%20the%20linking%20of%20pensions%20with%20the%20market%20and%20saw%20the%20move%20as%20a%20further%20depletion%20in%20employee%E2%80%99s%20social%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20become%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20and%20opposition%20forces.%20Many%20opposition-ruled%20states%20like%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Punjab%20have%20already%20scrapped%20the%20NPS%20in%20favour%20of%20OPS.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20was%20largely%20credited%20to%20the%20grand-old%20party%E2%80%99s%20poll%20promise%20of%20implementing%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20joined%20the%20protest%20to%20support%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20declared%20his%20support%20for%20OPS%20at%20the%20site.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20fully%20supported%20the%20legitimate%20demand%20of%20the%20employee%20organisations%20associated%20with%20NMOPS.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20Congress%20government%20is%20formed%20in%20Haryana%2C%20we%20will%20immediately%20fulfill%20this%20demand%20of%20the%20employees%20for%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupporting%20the%20OPS%2C%20the%20Congress%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%E2%80%9COld%2