0%2C000%2C%20Errol%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20weren't%20worried%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I%20said%20'Look%2C%20it's%20just%20not%20worth%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Errol%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20surprising%20Elon%20wasn't%20concerned%20about%20the%20cost%3A%20%24180%2C000%20represented%20about%200.00006%25%20of%20Elon's%20%24278%20billion%20net%20worth%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20service%20facility%20here.%20There's%20no%20Tesla%20representation%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Errol%20added%2C%20explaining%20why%20he%20declined%20his%20son's%20offer.%20%26quot%3BNo%20charging%20stations.%20I%20said%2C%20'Please%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20between%20%243%2C300%20and%20%247%2C000%20to%20ship%20a%20vehicle%20from%20the%20US%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20automotive%20shipping%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.a1autotransport.com%2Fship-car-to-south-africa%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTo%2520South%2520Africa-%2CTypical%2520Shipping%2520Prices%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520How%2520Much%2520Does%2520It%2520Cost%253F%2Cfactors%2520that%2520affect%2520the%2520price.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA1%20Auto%20Transport.%3C%2Fa%3E%20South%20Africa%20charges%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trade.gov%2Fcountry-commercial-guides%2Fsouth-africa-import-tariffs%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520end%2520rate%2520for%2520apparel%2Coriginal%2520equipment%2520components%2520through%25202035.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25%25%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20automotive%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Errol%20said%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20model%20Elon%20wanted%20to%20send%2C%20some%20of%20Tesla's%20most%20expensive%20cars%20at%20the%20time%2C%20like%20the%20Model%20S%20Plaid%2C%20cost%20over%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20was%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20exchange.%20The%20billionaire%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20ahead%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Tesla%20has%20begun%20selling%20its%20EVs%20in%20Europe%20and%20China%2C%20the%20vehicles%20are%20not%20for%20sale%20in%20South%20Africa.%20Winstone%20Jordaan%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20GridCars%2C%20a%20South%20African%20electric%20vehicle%20charging%20station%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.com%2Fnews24%2Ftech-and-trends%2Fnews%2Fbuild-it-and-they-will-come-says-the-head-of-the-largest-ev-charging-station-network-in-sa-20230527%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20a%20local%20news%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20that%20there%20are%20about%201%2C500%20EVs%20and%20300%20charging%20stations%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%20For%20comparison%2C%20there%20are%201.7%20million%20EVs%20in%20use%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D68d7ec20d67fb01aa5fd0fc26ed926a6c4803b213d838826f974e60ba98efb66%26postID%3D651306b4d34cd129df376180%26postSlug%3Delon-musk-errol-musk-turned-down-free-tesla-cost-shipping-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hertz.com%252Fus%252Fen%252Fblog%252Felectric-vehicles%252Fhow-many-electric-cars-are-in-the-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Experian%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20over%20130%2C000%20public%20charging%20stations%20across%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20March%20data%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Froadshow%2Fnews%2Fhow-many-ev-charging-stations-are-there-in-the-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20as%20if%20Errol%20was%20left%20without%20a%20way%20to%20get%20around%3A%20He%20said%20he%20owns%20a%20Rolls-Royce%20and%20a%20sports%20car.%20Plus%2C%20he%20has%20a%20Ryan%20Navion%20plane%20that%20was%20built%20in%201947%2C%20which%20he%20likes%20to%20take%20out%20and%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20Rolls-Royces%2C%20since%