%2F01%2F30084709%2FIMG_1736-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%201921%2C%20M.K.%20Gandhi%20wrote%20a%20piece%20for%20his%20Gujarati%20weekly%20%3Cem%3ENavajivan%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20the%20title%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESanatani%20Hindu%20Etale%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20literary%20translates%20as%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20Gandhi%20feel%20a%20need%20to%20write%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%3F%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%2C%20as%20he%20mentioned%20in%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20his%20article%2C%20was%20being%20asked%20why%20he%20call%20himself%20an%20orthodox%20Sanatani%20Hindu%20and%20why%20he%20regarded%20himself%20as%20a%20Vaishnava.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20possible%20reason%2C%20which%20he%20did%20not%20explicitly%20mention%2C%20was%20the%20constant%20criticism%20he%20faced%20by%20factions%20of%20the%20orthodox%20Hindus%20and%20the%20periodical%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%3C%2Fem%3E%20isince%20the%20time%20of%20the%20first%20Antyaj%20(untouchable)%20conference%20at%20Godhra%20in%201917.%20Gandhi%20had%20not%20only%20gone%20to%20the%20Mahar%20compound%20and%20eaten%20with%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98untouchables%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20started%20a%20movement%20against%20untouchability.%20These%20developments%20brought%20unease%20among%20orthodox%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20periodical%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%3C%2Fem%3E%20criticised%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20at%20the%20Antyaj%20Conference%2C%20he%20wrote%20them%20a%20letter%20titled%20%E2%80%9CA%20stain%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20forehead%E2%80%9D.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20because%20of%20it%20(untouchability)%20that%2C%20now%20for%20two%20thousand%20years%2C%20Hinduism%20has%20been%20burdened%20with%20a%20load%20of%20sin%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%20I%20call%20such%20orthodoxy%20hypocrisy.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20free%20yourself%20of%20this%20hypocrisy.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20criticised%20quoting%20verses%20from%20the%20Manusmriti%20and%20other%20scriptures%20in%20defence%20of%20this%20orthodoxy.%20He%20further%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20number%20of%20verses%20in%20these%20scriptures%20are%20apocryphal%3B%20a%20number%20of%20them%20are%20quite%20meaningless.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22We%20Could%20Do%20With%20Putting%20on%20Gandhi's%20Glasses%20%E2%80%93%20Now%20Reduced%20to%20a%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Logo%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgandhi-jayanti-swachh-bharat-india%5C%22%3EWe%20Could%20Do%20With%20Putting%20on%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Glasses%20%E2%80%93%20Now%20Reduced%20to%20a%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Logo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%201920%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20a%20talk%20with%20a%20Vaishnava%20religious%20leader%20in%20Bombay.%20An%20account%20of%20this%20talk%20with%20a%20commentary%20on%20it%20had%20appeared%20in%20the%20periodical%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Gandhi%20responded%20to%20this%20in%20the%20December%20issue%20of%20%3Cem%3ENavajivan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20stand%20hypocrisy%20and%20sophistry.%20I%20saw%20in%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%3C%2Fem%3E%20an%20account%20of%20a%20talk%20I%20had%20with%20Maharajshri%2C%20as%20also%20the%20comments%20on%20it.%20I%20have%20been%20very%20much%20pained%20by%20both%E2%80%A6%20I%20see%20in%20both%20an%20attempt%2C%20deliberate%20or%20otherwise%2C%20to%20prove%20adharma%20to%20be%20dharma.%20I%20shall%20explain%20next%20time%20what%20this%20is.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExactly%2020%20days%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20this%20issue%2C%20on%20December%2025%2C%201920%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20Antyaj%20conference%20held%20along%20with%20the%20annual%20session%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20at%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20reiterated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20is%20a%20sin%20and%20should%20be%20eradicated.%20I%20look%20upon%20it%20as%20my%20duty%20to%20eradicate%20this%20sin%E2%80%A6The%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20is%20an%20excrescence%20on%20Hinduism.%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20is%20a%20great%20Satanism%20in%20Hinduism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20Hindu%20myself%20and%20I%20claim%20to%20be%20an%20orthodox%20one.%20It%20is%20my%20further%20claim%20that%20I%20am%20a%20sanatani%20Hindu.%20At%20present%20I%20am%20engaged%20in%20a%20great%20dispute%20with%20the%20Hindus%20in%20Gujarat.%20They%2C%20especially%20the%20Vaishnavas%2C%20reject%20my%20claim%20to%20be%20called%20a%20sanatani%20Hindu%2C%20but%20I%20cling%20to%20it%20and%20assert%20that%20I%20am%20one%E2%80%A6I%20have%20said%20to%20the%20Hindus%2C%20and%20say%20it%20again%20today%2C%20that%20till%20Hindu%20society%20is%20purged%20of%20this%20sin(untouchability)%2C%20swaraj%20is%20an%20impossibility%E2%80%A6While%20the%20practice%20remains%20in%20Hindu%20society%2C%20I%20feel%20ashamed%20and%20feel%20unhappy%20even%20to%20call%20myself%20a%20Hindu.%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20dispute%20mentioned%20in%20the%20above%20paragraphs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20speaking%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20organisation%20RSS%20had%20yet%20to%20be%20born%20in%201925.%20Nathuram%20Godse%20was%20ten%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20Gandhi%20wrote%20and%20published%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%3F%E2%80%9D.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20Gandhi%20called%20the%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20%3Cem%3Eadharma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20make%20any%20persons%20crawl%20on%20their%20stomach%2C%20to%20segregate%20them%2C%20to%20drive%20them%20to%20live%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%2C%20not%20to%20be%20concerned%20whether%20they%20live%20or%20die%2C%20to%20give%20them%20food%20left%20over%20by%20others%E2%80%94all%20this%20certainly%20cannot%20be%20religion..%E2%80%94this%20is%20not%20Hinduism.%20This%20is%20Dyerism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnyone%20practicing%20untouchability%20or%20discriminating%20others%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20caste%20cannot%20be%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%2C%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20Gandhi.%20It%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20no%20Dalit%20or%20member%20of%20a%20backward%20class%20has%20ever%20become%20the%20RSS%20sarasanghachalak%20(chief)%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201925.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20article%20Gandhi%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20the%20most%20important%20outward%20form%20of%20Hinduism%20is%20cow-protection.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20May%20issue%20of%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20not%20kill%20a%20human%20being%20for%20protection%20of%20a%20cow%2C%20as%20I%20will%20not%20kill%20a%20cow%20for%20saving%20a%20human%20life%2C%20be%20it%20ever%20so%20precious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98I%20Look%20Upon%20an%20Increase%20of%20the%20Power%20of%20the%20State%20With%20the%20Greatest%20Fear%E2%80%99%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fi-look-upon-an-increase-of-the-power-of-the-state-with-the-greatest-fear%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Look%20Upon%20an%20Increase%20of%20the%20Power%20of%20the%20State%20With%20the%20Greatest%20Fear%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20cow-protection%20had%20deep%20interpretations.%20He%20often%20wrote%20on%20cow%20protection%20in%20later%20issues%20of%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CRishis%20declared%20that%20cow%20protection%20was%20the%20supreme%20duty%20of%20a%20Hindu%20and%20it%20brought%20one%20Moksha%20(Salvation).%20Now%20I%20am%20not%20ready%20to%20believe%20that%20by%20merely%20protecting%20the%20animal%20cow%2C%20one%20can%20attain%20moksha.%20For%20moksha%20one%20must%20completely%20get%20rid%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20lower%20feelings%20like%20attachment%2C%20hatred%2C%20anger%2C%20jealousy%2C%20etc%E2%80%A6cow%20protection%E2%80%A6from%20its%20very%20nature%20include%20the%20protection%20of%20everything%20that%20feels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20was%20clear%2C%20cow%20vigilantes%20involved%20in%20lynching-killing%20can%20be%20anything%20but%20sanatani%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20article%2C%20Gandhi%20explained%20his%20understanding%20of%20the%20scriptures.%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20claim%20to%20have%20fully%20read%20even%20a%20single%20Veda.%20Nevertheless%2C%20I%20have%20understood%20the%20shastras%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20dharma.%20I%20have%20grasped%20their%20real%20meaning.%20I%20know%20that%20one%20can%20attain%20moksha%20without%20reading%20the%20Vedas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlmost%2015%20years%20later%2C%20in%20a%201936%20issue%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20Harijan%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gandhi%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20exercise%20my%20judgement%20about%20every%20scripture%2C%20including%20the%20Bhagavadgita.%20I%20can%20not%20let%20a%20scriptural%20text%20supersede%20my%20reason.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20issue%20of%20%3Cem%3EHarijan%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20same%20year%2C%20an%20interesting%20conversation%20between%20C.F.%20Andrews%20and%20Gandhi%20got%20published.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20you%20are%20going%20to%20accept%20the%20position%20of%20mutual%20toleration%20or%20of%20equality%20of%20religions.%20My%20position%20is%20that%20all%20the%20great%20religions%20are%20fundamentally%20equal.%20We%20must%20have%20innate%20respect%20for%20other%20religions%20as%20we%20have%20for%20our%20own.%20Mind%20you%2C%20not%20mutual%20toleration%2C%20but%20equal%20respect%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20evening%20of%20January%2030%2C%201948%2C%20Gandhi%2C%2078-year-old%20man%2C%20frail%20due%20to%20fasting%2C%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20a%20prayer%20meeting%20when%20a%20fanatic%20Hindu%2C%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20fired%20three%20rounds%20of%20bullets%20at%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHey%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20were%20the%20last%20words%20from%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20outcome%20of%20Sanatani%20Hindu%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20charisma%20that%20Periyar%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%20and%20once%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%2C%20passed%20on%20a%20few%20recommendations%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20after%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20death.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20the%20name%20of%20India%20can%20be%20changed%20as%20Gandhi%20Desam%20or%20Gandhistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehul%20Devkala%20is%20a%20poet%20and%20an%20award-winning%20filmmaker.%20His%20short%20film%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fwatch-mehul-devkalas-award-winning-documentary-kaun-se-bapu%5C%22%3EKaun%20Se%20Bapu%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20based%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696234914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30084709%2FIMG_1736-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwho-is-a-sanatani-hindu-heres-what-gandhi-had-to-say%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anyone%20practicing%20untouchability%20or%20discriminating%20others%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20caste%20cannot%20be%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%2C%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20Gandhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwho-is-a-sanatani-hindu-heres-what-gandhi-had-to-say%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20can%20actually%20make%20workers%20perform%20worse%2C%20a%20new%20study%20found%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20student%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650d682412dc4f001a17b266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221803%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20using%20AI%20like%20ChatGPT%20