0In%202020%2C%20she%20started%20living%20in%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20and%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%2C%20the%20civil%20services%20entrance%20exam%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSurendra%20used%20to%20call%20her%20'beta'%20and%20took%20care%20of%20her.%20We%20never%20suspected%20anything.%20Then%20Mona%20went%20missing%20in%202021.%20We%20asked%20Surendra%2C%20but%20he%20said%20he%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20her%20whereabouts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Mona's%20sister%20registered%20a%20missing%20complaint%20at%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20police%20station.%20Surendra%20accompanied%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20constable%20put%20in%20motion%20an%20intricate%20plan%20to%20cover%20up%20his%20crime%20by%20convincing%20Mona's%20family%20that%20she%20was%20alive%2C%20but%20did%20not%20want%20her%20family%20to%20contact%20her.%20He%20got%20his%20brother-in-law%20Rabin%20to%20call%20up%20Mona's%20family%20members.%20Rabin%20introduced%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3BArvind%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20and%20Mona%20had%20married%2C%20but%20were%20hiding%20because%20his%20family%20was%20opposed%20to%20their%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20suspicious.%20Why%20wasn't%20Mona%20speaking%20to%20us%3F%20She%20was%20an%20educated%20woman%20and%20we%20had%20never%20stopped%20her%20from%20doing%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20sister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurendra%2C%20she%20said%2C%20would%20send%20Mona's%20family%20audio%20recordings%20in%20which%20he%20was%20heard%20asking%20her%20to%20return%20home.%20The%20cop%20had%20some%20audio%20clips%20in%20Mona's%20voice.%20He%20would%20edit%20them%20to%20add%20his%20voice%20and%20simulate%20a%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20travelled%20across%20five%20states%20to%20look%20for%20my%20sister.%20Every%20time%20her%20ATM%20card%20was%20used%2C%20I%20would%20go%20to%20that%20state.%20When%20I%20saw%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20ATM%20kiosks%2C%20I%20would%20see%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20helmet.%20Surendra%20would%20share%20information%20about%20hotels%20or%20dhabas%20and%20I%20would%20rush%20to%20them%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20Mona%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20her%20sister%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20school%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20not%20get%20leave%20daily%20to%20look%20for%20my%20sister.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20I%20would%20finish%20work%2C%20go%20to%20police%20stations%20for%20information%20about%20Mona.%20Some%20days%2C%20it%20would%20get%20so%20late%20that%20I%20could%20not%20even%20go%20home.%20I%20returned%20to%20school%20in%20the%20same%20clothes%20as%20the%20fay%20before.%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20I%20got%20information%20that%20Mona%20was%20in%20Karnataka.%20I%20took%20leave%20and%20travelled%20there.%20Now%20I%20know%20the%20call%20was%20made%20by%20Surendra's%20wife%20Rabin%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20draw%20Mona's%20family%20deeper%20into%20his%20web%20of%20lies%2C%20Surendra%20got%20a%20woman%20vaccinated%20and%20got%20a%20Covid%20jab%20certificate%20in%20Mona's%20name.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20started%20suspecting%20Surendra%2C%20but%20we%20had%20no%20proof.%20When%20we%20spoke%20to%20the%20cops%20at%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20police%20station%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'your%20sister%20has%20eloped'.%20Our%20family%20was%20shattered%2C%20but%20I%20did%20not%20lose%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20fighting%20back%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20after%20she%20registered%20the%20missing%20complaint%2C%20a%20case%20was%20filed%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20breakthrough%20whatsoever.%20Two%20months%20back%2C%20Mona's%20sister%20met%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora%20and%20shared%20her%20heart-rending%20account.%20The%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20crime%20branch%2C%20which%20cracked%20it%20within%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%20is%20now%20waiting%20for%20strict%20punishment%20for%20the%20accused.%20She%20has%20requested%20seni