ers%20of%20the%20World!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added%20in%20another%20July%204%2C%202013%20tweet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20in%202020%2C%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2020%2Faug%2F21%2Fdonald-trump-sharks-speech-stormy-daniels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20supporters%20at%20a%20rally%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he's%20not%20on%20board%20with%20protecting%20sharks%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20saying%20the%20other%20night%2C%20the%20shark.%20They%20were%20saying%2C%20'Sharks%2C%20we%20have%20to%20protect%20them.'%20I%20said%2C%20'Wait%20a%20minute%2C%20wait.'%20They%20actually%20want%20to%20remove%20all%20the%20seals%20in%20order%20to%20save%20the%20shark.%20I%20said%2C%20'Wait%2C%20don't%20you%20have%20it%20the%20other%20way%20around%3F'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20sharks%20either.%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20how%20many%20votes%20am%20I%20going%20to%20lose%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStormy%20Daniels%2C%20the%20adult%20film%20actress%20to%20whom%20Trump%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indicted-new-york-stormy-daniels-hush-money-payment-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20accused%20of%20giving%20a%20pre-election%20hush%20money%20payment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20has%20told%20multiple%20media%20outlets%20that%20the%20former%20president%20watches%20%26quot%3BShark%20Week%26quot%3B%20programs%20but%20is%20terrified%20of%20the%20oceanic%20predators.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20arriving%2C%20and%20he%20was%20watching%20Shark%20Week.%20He%20made%20me%20sit%20and%20watch%20an%20entire%20documentary%20about%20shark%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20told%20Anderson%20Cooper%20in%20