0dynamics%20at%20play%2C%20ranging%20from%20maintaining%20the%20competitive%20advantage%2C%20reducing%20the%20production%20costs%20and%20increasing%20efficiency%20to%20quality%20and%20innovation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIEO%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20spike%20in%20export%20growth%20of%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fexports-up-23-52-to-40-billion-in-june-trade-deficit-at-record-26-billion-news-209279%5C%22%3E%2440%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20due%20to%20a%20rerouting%20of%20crude%20oil%20trade%20routes%20via%20India%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20woven%20garments%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20export%20growth%20has%20consistently%20been%20below%201%25%20for%20years%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20a%20global%20trade%20growth%20rate%20of%20about%202%25.%20Bangladesh%20and%20Vietnam%20are%20growing%20at%206%25%20and%204%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20footwear%20sector%2C%20the%20global%20trade%20expanded%20by%205%25%2C%20but%20India%E2%80%99s%20exports%20have%20contracted.%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20growth%20from%20%241%20billion%20to%20%241.7%20billion%20over%20three%20years%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20meagre%20growth%20from%20about%20%242.8%20billion%20to%20%243%20billion%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20pharmacy%20sector%20as%20well%2C%20the%20sector%E2%80%99s%20growth%20has%20not%20matched%20demand%2C%20lagging%20at%209%25%20while%20the%20global%20market%20grew%20by%2012%25%20in%20the%20past%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConcerns%20arose%20due%20to%20criticism%20linked%20to%20cough%20syrup%2C%20underlining%20the%20need%20for%20an%20efficient%20trace%20and%20tracking%20system%20for%20quality%20assurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20technology-driven%20sector%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20the%20global%20demand%20for%20machinery%2C%20auto%20components%2C%20electrical%20and%20electronics%20goods%2C%C2%A0%20India%E2%80%99s%20current%20market%20share%20in%20these%20sectors%20stands%20at%20a%20mere%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20labour-intensive%20sectors%20raises%20concerns%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20competitiveness%20and%20sustained%20participation%20in%20these%20traditional%20jobs%20creating%20crucial%20segments%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20goods%20exports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fgoods-exports-decline-6-9-year-on-year-in-august-due-to-weak-external-demand-report%5C%22%3Econtracted%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20seventh%20straight%20month%20in%20August%20though%20the%20extent%20of%20decline%20narrowed%20to%206.86%25%20from%20double-digit%20contractions%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20to%20hit%20a%20three-month%20high%20of%20%2434.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20FIEO%20president%20A.%20Sakthivel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Findias-goods-exports-shrinks-in-august%2Farticle67311193.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20easy%20and%20cheaper%20credit%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20small%20enterprises.%20They%20also%20need%20marketing%20support%20such%20as%20promoting%20Indian%20products%20as%20well%20as%20exempting%20GST%20levies%20on%20freight%20for%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696229015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19151431%2Fimage-920.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-share-in-global-exports-in-labour-intensive-sectors-declining-says-top-exporters-body%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Export%20Organisations%20said%20that%20the%20most%20%26quot%3Bpressing%20concern%26quot%3B%20regarding%20the%20negative%20export%20growth%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20performance%20of%20labour-in