leanliness%20mission%20with%20a%20logo%20in%20which%20one%20lens%20of%20a%20pair%20of%20glasses%20has%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98Swachh%E2%80%99%20written%20on%20it%20and%20the%20other%20has%20%E2%80%98Bharat%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20two%20words%20written%20on%20the%20two%20lenses%20block%20our%20vision%20to%20a%20considerable%20extent%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20understanding%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20holistic%20ideals%20which%20affirmed%20an%20all%20encompassing%20worldview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20threat%20to%20communal%20unity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20defining%20aspects%20of%20his%20extraordinary%20life%2C%20marked%20with%20the%20arduous%20quest%20for%20freedom%2C%20was%20to%20promote%20communal%20unity%20and%20harmony%20cutting%20across%20all%20faiths%20and%20other%20primordial%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20lived%20an%20exemplary%20life%20upholding%20communal%20harmony%20and%20eventually%20laid%20down%20his%20life%20in%20defence%20of%20that%20cherished%20ideal.%20Had%20Gandhi%20been%20alive%20today%20he%20would%20have%20been%20distressed%20to%20see%20the%20laws%20enacted%20in%20several%20BJP-ruled%20states%20of%20our%20country%20to%20target%20the%20so%20called%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20very%20coercively%20deal%20with%20the%20inter-faith%20couples%20bound%20by%20matrimonial%20ties%20or%20aspiring%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20laws%20enacted%20to%20prevent%20people%20to%20opt%20for%20matrimonial%20relations%20cutting%20across%20faiths%20is%20severe%20blow%20to%20communal%20unity%20which%20Gandhi%20flagged%20as%20indispensable%20to%20make%20India%20free%20from%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20regime%20initially%20took%20a%20stand%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmha-says-centre-has-no-plans-to-bring-countrywide-love-jihad-law%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20non-existent%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20statements%20to%20that%20effect%20were%20made%20in%20the%20parliament%20by%20senior%20ministers%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20several%20other%20%E2%80%98jihads%E2%80%99%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-demographic-probe-property-deals-land-jihad%5C%22%3Eland%20jihad%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsudarshan-news-upsc-jihad-muslims-governance%5C%22%3EUPSC%20jihad%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20have%20been%20coined%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20to%20exclude%20Muslims%20from%20the%20collective%20life%20and%20reduce%20them%20to%20a%20status%20where%20the%20constitutionally%20%C2%A0guaranteed%20fundamental%20rights%20are%20denied%20to%20them%20with%20impunity.%20While%20%E2%80%98land%20jihad%E2%80%99%20misinterprets%20the%20legitimate%20settlements%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20land%20or%20area%20lawfully%20acquired%20by%20them%20as%20a%20method%20of%20conversion%2C%20%E2%80%98UPSC%20jihad%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20the%20entry%20of%20Muslims%20to%20civil%20service%20by%20qualifying%20in%20the%20written%20test%20and%20via%20voce%20conducted%20by%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsudarshan-news-tv-show-upsc-jihad-suresh-chavhanke-fact-check%5C%22%3EA%20List%20of%20All%20the%20False%20Claims%20Made%20in%20Sudarshan%20TV%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98UPSC%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20venomous%20interpretation%20given%20to%20the%20selection%20process%20based%20on%20merit%20and%20worth%20of%20candidates%20regardless%20of%20their%20faiths%20constitute%20an%20attempt%20to%20foster%20deep%20seated%20prejudice%20and%20hate%20against%20Muslims%20so%20that%20they%20get%20excluded%20from%20the%20civil%20service.%20Never%20ever%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20have%20such%20vicious%20and%20venomous%20terms%20been%20coined%20to%20exclude%20a%20section%20of%20citizens%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20faith%20and%20assault%20the%20unity%20of%20our%20people%20professing%20diverse%20faiths.%20So%20the%20ruling%20regime%2C%20while%20invoking%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Swachh%20Bharat%2C%20is%20deliberately%20trying%20to%20push%20to%20oblivion%20the%20ideal%20of%20communal%20harmony%20which%20constituted%20the%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20architecture%20of%20Swaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-300x210.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748-1024x715.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-638156%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETea%20and%20water%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20with%20anguish%20about%20the%20obnoxious%20practice%20prevailing%20in%20pre-Independent%20India%20where%20vendors%20in%20public%20places%20and%20railway%20stations%20used%20to%20sell%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20tea%E2%80%9D%20separate%20from%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20tea%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20%3Cem%3Epani%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20water%E2%80%9D%2C%20separate%20from%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20pani.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20wondered%20how%20unity%20among%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20would%20be%20established%20if%20the%20division%20was%20so%20deep%20that%20even%20water%20and%20tea%20got%20divided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20binaries.%20He%20wrote%20in%20his%20booklet%20%3Cem%3EConstructive%20Programme%3A%20Its%20Meaning%20and%20Place%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20in%20early%201940s%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20thing%20essential%20for%20achieving%20such%20unity%20is%20for%20every%20Congressman%2C%20whatever%20his%20religion%20may%20be%2C%20to%20represent%20in%20his%20own%20person%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20Zoroastrian%2C%20Jew%2C%20etc.%2C%20shortly%2C%20every%20Hindu%20and%20non-Hindu%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20pleaded%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20realize%20this%2C%20every%20Congressman%20will%20cultivate%20personal%20friendship%20with%20persons%20representing%20faiths%20other%20than%20his%20own%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERemarking%20that%20such%20regard%20for%20the%20faiths%20of%20others%20would%20create%20a%20happy%20situation%20and%20there%20would%20be%20no%20disgraceful%20cry%20at%20the%20stations%2C%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20water%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20water%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20tea%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20tea%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20described%20the%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20Congress%20men%20as%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20revolution%20which%20should%20have%20no%20political%20%C2%A0motive%20and%20persuasively%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20unity%20will%20be%20its%20natural%20fruit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20note%20that%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20tea%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20tea%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20pani%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20pani%2C%E2%80%99%20were%20being%20sold%20in%20pre-Independent%20India%20not%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20by%20products%20of%20religious%20prejudices%20which%20often%20got%20manifested%20in%20divisive%20narratives%2C%20impacting%20several%20aspects%20including%20beverages.%20Had%20Gandhi%20been%20alive%20he%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20to%20note%20that%20in%20independent%20India%20the%20practice%20of%20selling%20water%20and%20tea%20thus%20is%20no%20longer%20prevalent.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20deeply%20hurt%20to%20note%20that%20in%20the%20BJP-ruled%20state%20governments%20have%20employed%20legislation%20and%20taken%20administrative%20decisions%20against%20the%20bogeys%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ffocus-on-love-jihad-not-small-issues-like-roads-drains-bjp-karnataka-chief-to-party-workers%5C%22%3Elove%20jihad%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtarakhand-demographic-probe-property-deals-land-jihad%5C%22%3Eland%20jihad%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-leaders-dharma-sansad-muslim-genocide%5C%22%3EHindutva%20leaders%20called%20for%20genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20comprehensive%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20frightening%20developments%20endangering%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20India%20are%20sustained%20by%20relentless%20spread%20of%20hate.%20Those%20controlling%20the%20state%20apparatus%20are%20maintaining%20a%20deafening%20silence%20on%20the%20issue.%20This%20is%20so%20in%20spite%20of%20some%20of%20the%20recent%20judgements%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20states%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-justice-joseph-nagarathna-hate-speech-religion%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520the%2520role%2520of%2520contempt%2520in%2520dealing%2520with%2520this%2520particular%2Corders%2520have%2520to%2520be%2520implemented.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3Emust%20take%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20cognisance%20of%20hate%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20adopt%20strict%20legal%20steps%20to%20neutralise%20the%20threat%20arising%20out%20of%20those%20sordid%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20powers%20that%20be%20spin%20communal%20narratives%20and%20subtly%20use%20them%20as%20dog%20whistles%20to%20target%20minorities.%20A%20helpful%20media%20then%20transmits%20hatred%20day%20in%20day%20and%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPermeation%20of%20hatred%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHate%20has%20permeated%20to%20deeper%20levels%20of%20society%20and%20larger%20collective%20life%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20that%20it%20was%20recently%20manifested%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%5C%22%3Ethree%20Muslim%20passengers%20in%20a%20moving%20train%20by%20a%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RPF)%20constable%20who%2C%20it%20is%20understood%2C%20identified%20them%20by%20their%20religion%20and%20shot%20them.%20He%20had%20also%20reportedly%20stated%20that%20to%20stay%20in%20India%20one%20has%20to%20vote%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHate%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%20was%20evidenced%20in%20an%20ominous%20manner%20in%20a%20class%20room%20in%20a%20school%20in%20UP%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-teacher-forces-fellow-students-to-slap-muslim-child-ncpcr-orders-not-to-circulate-video%5C%22%3Ea%20Muslim%20boy%20was%20beaten%20by%20his%20classmates%20on%20the%20express%20instructions%20of%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20faith%20of%20that%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20used%20abusive%20language%20against%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20made%20highly%20derogatory%20remarks%20on%20account%20of%20his%20Islamic%20identity.%20Even%20though%20all%20those%20remarks%20have%20been%20expunged%20from%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20House%20by%20the%20Speaker%20he%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20agai