verify%20who%20Kochevnik%20called%20and%20when%20that%20call%20took%20place.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKochevnik%20first%20called%20up%20a%20person%20he%20said%20was%20a%20Uralvagonzavod%20staff%20member%2C%20Aleksander%20Anatolevich.%20On%20the%20call%2C%20Kochevnik%20ran%20through%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints%20about%20the%20tank%2C%20from%20how%20it%20had%20been%20spewing%20oil%20to%20its%20faulty%20compressors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20commander%20of%20an%20armor%20group%20and%20the%20problem%20is%20we%20simply%20cannot%20operate%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kochevnik%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20per%20Forbes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnatolevich%20appeared%20to%20be%20unaware%20that%20he%20was%20speaking%20to%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier.%20He%20assured%20Kochevnik%20that%20he%20would%20raise%20Kochevnik's%20issues%20with%20the%20design%20bureau%20and%20the%20engine%20manufacturer%2C%20per%20Forbes'%20translation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20video%2C%20Kochevnik%20made%20a%20call%20to%20what%20he%20claimed%20was%20Uralvagonzavod%20director%20Andrey%20Abakumov.%20Abakumov%20could%20be%20heard%20telling%20Kochevnik%20to%20report%20the%20tank's%20issues%20via%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%2C%20per%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Anatolevich%2C%20Abakumov%20seemed%20to%20be%20unaware%20that%20Kochevnik%20was%20Ukrainian.%20Kochevnik%20later%20revealed%20his%20identity%20to%20both%20men%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I'm%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20armored%20group%20K-2.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20mechanized%20battalion%20of%20Ukraine's%2054th%20mechanized%20brigade%2C%26quot%3B%20Kochevnik%20told%20Anatolevich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20take%20more%20of%20these%20tanks%20as%20our%20trophies%2C%20make%20them%20better%20so%20that%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20for%20us%20to%20operate%20them.%20Agreed%3F%20Thank%20you%20very%20much.%20Take%20care%20of%20yourselves.%20Glory%20to%20Ukraine%2C%26quo