h%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Urdu%20%E2%80%94%20which%20covered%20that%20moment%20of%20the%20killing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20of%20looking%20back%20at%20a%20key%20moment%20in%20our%20history%2C%20but%20through%20a%20different%20lens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20research%2C%20Rahman%20and%20his%20team%20chose%20to%20release%20the%20exhibition%20now%20given%20current%20attitudes%20toward%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%20In%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20has%20become%20a%20polarising%20historical%20event%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsecret-worship-of-nathuram-godse-public-salute-to-mahatma-gandhi%2Fcid%2F1961993%5C%22%3Esome%20Hindu%20nationalists%20praising%20Nathuram%20Godse%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fncert-deletions-about-gandhis-assassination-show-how-shrewdly-the-operation-was-planned%5C%22%3ENCERT%20deleting%20texts%20relating%20to%20the%20assassination%20in%20school%20textbooks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20of%20reminding%20people%20of%20who%20killed%20Gandhi%20and%20why%2C%20because%20history%20is%20being%20re-written%2C%20re-interpreted%20in%20a%20very%20shallow%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20thought%20that%20this%20is%20a%20good%20way%20of%20bringing%20some%20kind%20of%20memory%2C%20particularly%20to%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98The%20Light%20Has%20Gone%20Out%20%E2%80%94%20Photography%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Assassination%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20open%20to%20the%20public%20from%20October%202%20to%20October%2021%20at%20Jawahar%20Bhawan%20in%20Delhi.%20Rahman%20said%20he%20has%20designed%20it%20as%20a%20travelling%20exhibition%20and%20hopes%20it%20can%20be%20displayed%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYasmeen%20Saadi%20is%20an%20intern%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696224454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02105135%2FPanel-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fa-photography-exhibition-looks-at-gandhis-assassination-through-a-new-lens%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CIt's%20a%20way%20of%20reminding%20people%20of%20who%20killed%20Gandhi%20and%20why%2C%20because%20history%20is%20being%20re-written%2C%20re-interpreted%20in%20a%20very%20shallow%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20curator%20Ram%20Rahman%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fa-photography-exhibition-looks-at-gandhis-assassination-through-a-new-lens%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBSE%20Opposes%20Uniform%20Education%20System%2C%20Highlights%20%26quot%3BLocal%20Culture%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20has%20opposed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20that%20demanded%20a%20uniform%20education%20system%20across%20the%20country%20up%20to%20Class%2012.%20In%20its%20reply%2C%20the%20board%20told%20the%20court%20that%20since%20education%20is%20a%20subject%20in%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20schools%20being%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20state%20governments%2C%20it%20is%20for%20the%20respective%20state%2FUnion%20Territory%20governments%20to%20frame%20syllabus%2C%20curriculum%20and%20conduct%20examinations%20for%20their%20schools.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Advocating%20for%20introducing%20education%20in%20mother%20tongue%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20the%20board%20noted%20that%20the%20uniform%20board%2Fsyllabus%20across%20India%20does%20not%20take%20into%20account%20the%20local%20context%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20language.%3Cbr%3E%20Further%20emphasising%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20including%20local%20resources%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20ethos%20in%20the%20curriculum%2C%20the%20CBSE%20said%20that%20a%20child%20can%20better%20relate%20to%20a%20course%20that%20is%20more%20closely%20related%20to%20his%2Fher%20life%20outside%20the%20school.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20multiplicity%20of%20curricula%20and%20other%20educational%20resources%20is%20desirable%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20core%20common%20element.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20petition%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20Mr%20Upadhyay's%2C%20a%20practising%20lawyer%20and%20BJP%20leader%2C%20said%20while%20syllabus%20and%20curriculum%20are%20common%20for%20all%20entrance%20examinations%2C%20the%20syllabus%20and%20curriculum%20of%20the%20CBSE%2C%20Indian%20Certificate%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20and%20state%20boards%20are%20totally%20different.%20Thus%2C%20students%20do%20not%20get%20equal%20opportunity%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20Articles%2014-16%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20provide%20equal%20opportunity%20to%20all%20students%20as%20the%20syllabus-curriculum%20of%20CBSE%2C%20ICSE%2C%20and%20State%20Board%20is%20totally%20different.%20Although%20harmonious-purposive%20construction%20of%20Articles%2014%2C%2015%2C%2016%2C%2021%2C%2021A%20with%20Articles%2038%2C%2039%2C%2046%20confirms%20that%20education%20is%20the%20most%20important%20fundamental%20right%20and%20the%20state%20cannot%20discriminate%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20region%2C%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20class%20or%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Upadhyay%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20this%20disparity%20cannot%20be%20fully%20removed%2C%20the%20government%20can%20establish%20a%20standardised%20entrance%20system%20for%20college%20and%20university%20aspirants.%20Standardisation%20of%20syllabus%20and%20curriculum%20means%20that%20everyone%20would%20have%20equal%20chances%20of%20getting%20into%20colleges%20and%20universities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioner%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20education%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20must%20be%20at%20the%20same%20level%20and%20similar%20standard%2C%20and%20not%20based%20on%20the%20child's%20socioeconomic%20conditions.%20The%20children%20have%20the%20right%20to%20avail%20free%20compulsory%20and%20common%20education%20irrespective%20of%20their%20social-economic%20religious%20and%20cultural%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20plea.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20textbooks%20set%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20In%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20the%20National%20Curriculum%20Framework%20(NCF)%20developed%20by%20the%20NCERT%20sets%20the%20guidelines%20and%20the%20two%20are%20responsible%20for%20developing%20curriculum%2C%20syllabi%2C%20textbooks%2C%20and%20other%20supplementary%20materials%20for%20schools%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20State%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(SCERTs)%20and%20State%20Education%20Boards%20either%20adopt%20or%20adapt%20NCERT's%20model%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20or%20develop%20their%20own%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20based%20on%20NCF%2C%20stated%20CBSE.%3Cbr%3E%20The%20CBSE%20said%20that%20the%20present%20writ%20petition%20seeking%20a%20uniform%20education%20system%20across%20the%20country%20is%20devoid%20of%20merits%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696223940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F6hk08tf8_cbse-board-exam-2023-datesheet_625x300_30_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-opposes-common-syllabus-across-india-it-does-not-take-into-account-4441902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20board's%20reply%2