m%20Clark%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Thistle%20Marine%2C%20in%20Peterhead%2C%20Aberdeenshire%20dismissed%20her%20medical%20problem%20and%20told%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bjust%20get%20on%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-north-east-orkney-shetland-66962519%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20sued%20the%20company%20for%20unfair%20dismissal%20and%20harassment.%20She%20described%20her%2072-year-old%20boss%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdinosaur%26quot%3B%20who%20didn't%20move%20with%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20known%20this%20company%20for%2027%20years%20and%20they%20treated%20me%20like%20rubbish.%20Mr%20Clark%20didn't%20like%20change.%20He%20didn't%20like%20being%20challenged%20on%20things.%20He%20didn't%20move%20with%20the%20times.%20I%20tried%20to%20explain%20some%20issues%20in%20what%20you%20can%20say%20and%20what%20you%20can't%20say%20and%20it%20just%20fell%20on%20deaf%20ears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20two%20also%20said%20that%20the%20boss%20would%20%26quot%3Boften%20refer%20to%20employees%20who%20were%20off%20sick%20as%20'snowflakes'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Clark%20founded%20Thistle%20Marine%20in%20the%20late%201970s.%20The%20tribunal%20in%20Aberdeen%20heard%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20the%20woman%20told%20her%20boss%20that%20she%20had%20menopause%20symptoms.%20She%20was%20suffering%20from%20anxiety%2C%20loss%20of%20concentration%20and%20brain%20fog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20she%20worked%20from%20home%20for%20two%20days%2C%20%C2%A0first%20due%20to%20heavy%20snow%20and%20then%20because%20of%20her%20menopausal%20bleeding.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20she%20arrived%20in%20the%20office%20at%20around%202%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20passed%20Mr%20Clark%20in%20the%20corridor%20and%20he%20spoke%20to%20her%20in%20a%20sarcastic%20tone%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20see%20you've%20made%20it%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Farquharson%20explained%20her%20situation.%20The%20tribunal%20heard%20that%20Mr%20Clark%20gave%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisgusted%20look%26quot%3B.%20The%2049-year-old%20was%20upset%20and%20angry%20at%20the%20implication%20and%20decided%20to%20confront%20Mr%20Clark.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Clark%20dismissed%20her%20menopausal%20symptoms%20and%20said%20everybody%20has%20%26quot%3Baches%20and%20pains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tribunal%2C%20Mr%20Clark%20said%20that%20the%20remarks%20were%20%26quot%3Binnocent%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20Ms%20Farquharson%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20money%20ahead%20of%20her%20wedding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJim%20Clark%20can%20best%20be%20described%20as%20a%20blunt%2C%20self-made%20man%20and%20successful%20businessman.%20He%20no%20doubt%20has%20many%20admirable%20qualities%20but%20empathy%20for%20others%20is%20not%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20clear%20to%20us%20that%20he%20has%20little%20time%20or%20respect%20for%20those%2C%20unlike%20himself%2C%20who%20are%20not%20able%20to%20work%20as%20hard%20or%20without%20illness%20as%20he%20has.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20remarks%20to%20Ms%20Farquharson%20violated%20her%20dignity%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20panel%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696223160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd27p7r1o_karen-farquharson-with-husband_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscottish-woman-wins-rs-37-lakh-payout-over-boss-menopause-comments-4441878%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mother%20of%20two%20also%20said%20that%20the%20boss%20would%20%26quot%3Boften%20refer%20to%20employees%20who%20were%20off%20sick%20as%20'snowflakes'%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22can