20that%20is%20impacting%20some%20users%20and%20will%20be%20addressed%20in%20a%20software%20update.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20told%20Bloomberg%20it%20is%20working%20with%20developers%20behind%20the%20apps%20causing%20the%20iPhone%20to%20overheat%20and%20that%20fixes%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20released.%20A%20spokesman%20said%20that%20Instagram%20from%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%2C%20Uber%20Technologies%20Inc.'s%20app%20and%20the%20game%20Asphalt%209%20have%20caused%20the%20device%20to%20run%20warmer%20than%20normal.%20Instagram%20already%20mitigated%20the%20problem%20with%20its%20app%20on%20Sept.%2027%2C%20Apple%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20high-end%20device%20includes%20a%20titanium%20frame%2C%20a%20first%20for%20the%20iPhone%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20A17%20Pro%20chip%20with%20enhanced%20graphics%20component%20for%20improved%20gaming.%20Some%20researchers%20said%20those%20hardware%20changes%20could%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Apple%20denied%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20related%20to%20the%20hardware%20of%20the%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20line%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20new%20design%20results%20in%20improved%20heat%20dissipation%20compared%20to%20prior%20stainless%20steel%20devices.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20the%20upcoming%20software%20fix%20will%20not%20involve%20slowing%20down%20the%20processor%20of%20the%20latest%20models.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20said%20the%20issue%20is%20not%20a%20safety%20problem%20and%20will%20not%20impact%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20iPhone%20longterm.%20It%20added%20that%20USB-C%20charging%2C%20the%20new%20standard%20included%20with%20the%20latest%20models%2C%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20of%20the%20issue.%20It%20did%2C%20however%2C%20say%20that%20the%20use%20of%20a%20large%20charging%20adapter%20-%20those%20that%20offer%20speeds%20above%2020%20watts%20-%20could%20cause%20iPhones%20to%20temporarily%20feel%20hotter%20than%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20users%20have%20complained%20on%20social%20media%20and%20to%20Apple%20support%20that%20their%20new%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20and%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20Max%20can%20feel%20abnormally%20hot%20to%20the%20touch.%20Some%20users%20have%20even%20posted%20photos%20of%20a%20thermometer%20reading%20of%20their%20iPhone%2C%20showing%20results%20of%20well%20over%20100F%20(38C).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApple%20didn't%20say%20when%20the%20iOS%2017%20software%20update%20would%20be%20available%20or%20which%20version%20it%20would%20carry.%20The%20company%20last%20week%20released%20the%20first%20beta%20version%20of%20iOS%2017.1%20to%20app%20developers.%20That%20release%20is%20scheduled%20for%20later%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696221900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fcdvg5d0g_apple-iphone-15-generic-afp_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbugs-apps-software-apple-lists-reasons-behind-iphone-overheating-4441842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20Inc.%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20recent%20claims%20of%20new%20iPhones%20getting%20too%20hot%20to%20the%20touch%20are%20due%20to%20software%20and%20app-related%20bugs%20and%20that%20fixes%20are%20coming%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbugs-apps-software-apple-lists-reasons-behind-iphone-overheating-4441842%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbugs-apps-software-apple-lists-reasons-behind-iphone-overheating-4441842%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbugs-apps-software-apple-lists-reasons-behind-iphone-overheating-4441842%2Famp%2F1%22%