trike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696219109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLast-Week-Tonight-Writers-Strike-e1696218715428.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235741906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CLast%20Week%20Tonight%20With%20John%20Oliver%E2%80%9D%20made%20its%20return%20to%20the%20air%20after%20five%20months%20on%20Sunday%20following%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20writers%E2%80%99%20strike.%20Oliver%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20news%20to%20recap%20his%20first%20night%20back%2C%20doing%20quick%20riffs%20on%20everything%20from%20U.S.%20Rep.%20Lauren%20Boebert%20to%20a%20recent%20deposition%20involving%20Mike%20Lindell%2C%20but%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjohn-oliver-last-week-tonight-writers-strike-1235741906%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjohn-oliver-last-week-tonight-writers-strike-1235741906%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fjohn-oliver-last-week-tonight-writers-strike-1235741906%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20Fingers%20Can%20Create'%3A%20The%20Creative%20Possibilities%20of%20Gandhian%20Non-Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30124718%2FIMG_1738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201938%2C%20the%20Seva%20Sangh%2C%20under%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20broad%20directions%20arranged%20a%20rural%20industries%20and%20crafts%20fair%20in%20Beraboi%20village%20of%20Delang%20in%20Orissa.%20Delang%20was%20a%20railway%20station%20in%20pre-Independence%20times%2C%20not%20far%20from%20Puri%20town.%20Many%20livelihood%20activities%20were%20showcased%20in%20Beraboi%20that%20year%20with%20help%20from%20the%20provincial%20government%2C%20Puri%20Zilla%20Board%2C%20and%20several%20cooperative%20societies.%C2%A0%20Orissa%20had%20been%20declared%20a%20separate%20province%20just%20two%20years%20prior%2C%20after%20a%20long%20and%20sustained%20language-based%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%202%2C60%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20Beraboi%20exhibition%20was%20laid%20out%20in%20five%20separate%20galleries%20%E2%80%93%20Khadi%2C%20Village%20Industries%2C%20Health%20and%20Education%2C%20Farming%2C%20and%20the%20Arts.%20Craftworks%20made%20from%20ivory%20and%20brass%20and%20statues%20of%20the%20Buddha%20graced%20the%20arts%20stalls.%20Around%20300%20graphic%20posters%20providing%20information%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20topics%2C%20such%20as%20personal%20hygiene%20and%20alcohol%20consumption%20were%20arranged%20in%20the%20gallery%20marked%20Health%20and%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d29983.982605356017!2d85.73552537112515!3d20.05053380734445!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3a19b064d4184abf%253A0x6434a52592520ca3!2sBeraboi%252C%2520Odisha!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1696217419497!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20was%20Gandhi%20attending%20a%20week-long%20crafts%20fair%20in%20Orissa%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20national%20level%2C%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20who%20was%20challenging%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20been%20elected%20Congress%20president%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier.%C2%A0%20The%20ongoing%20Spanish%20Civil%20War%20and%20Second%20Sino-Japanese%20War%20were%20foreshadowing%20the%20outbreak%20of%20a%20major%20global%20conflict%2C%20which%20manifested%20itself%20as%20World%20War%20II%20a%20year%20later.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20when%20violence%20once%20again%20threatened%20to%20overwhelm%20the%20world%2C%20was%20Gandhi%20frittering%20away%20his%20time%20and%20energy%20at%20a%20fair%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20Orissa%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20public%20in%20the%20Beraboi%20fair%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAgriculture%20alone%20cannot%20help%20us.%20We%20cannot%20sustain%20ourselves%20without%20other%20allied%20enterprises.%20We%20can%20now%20see%20what%20fingers%20can%20create%20and%20how%20these%20creations%20can%20help%20us%20enhance%20our%20income%20as%20a%20nation.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20ask%20you%20to%20look%20at%20the%20exhibits%20again%20and%20again.%20Select%20one%20of%20the%20items%20on%20display.%20The%20(Seva)%20Sangh%20hopes%20each%20household%20turns%20into%20a%20factory%20of%20handmade%20products.%20Look%20at%20the%20exhibits%20like%20a%20student%20and%20learn%20something%20that%20helps%20you%20to%20serve%20Orissa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Beraboi%20conclave%20was%20not%20just%20a%20self-indulgent%20display%20in%20which%20the%20attendees%20were%20asked%20to%20behold%2C%20admire%2C%20and%20disperse.%20It%20also%20organised%20a%20seven-day-long%20seminar%20in%20which%20delegates%20debated%20everyday%20concerns.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20advantages%20of%20cow%20milk%20over%20buffalo%20milk%20were%20thoroughly%20debated%20by%20the%20speakers%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20large%20crowds.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20ingeniously%20devising%20ways%20of%20determining%20what%20we%20today%20call%20cost%20benefit%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20violent%20revolution%20could%20not%20have%20supported%20such%20a%20discourse%20because%20the%20atmosphere%20would%20be%20saturated%20with%20feelings%20of%20fear%2C%20anger%2C%20and%20revenge.%20Truth%20be%20told%2C%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20having%20debates%20within%20a%20mass%20movement%20seeking%20transformative%20change%20is%20only%20possible%20if%20it%20is%20non-violent.%20If%20Gandhi%20had%20been%20leading%20a%20militant%20resistance%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20little%20scope%20for%20a%20spirited%20public%20debate%20as%20was%20held%20in%20Beraboi.%20Discussions%20would%20have%20been%20held%20in%20secret%20and%20commands%20would%20have%20been%20imperiously%20handed%20down%20from%20the%20top.%20Violence%20demands%20compliance%2C%20whereas%20non-violence%20leaves%20room%20for%20debate%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20constructive%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInclusiveness%20is%20also%20another%20key%20characteristic%20of%20non-violence.%20In%201937%3Cstrong%3E%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOrissa%20province%20had%20formed%20a%20Congress-led%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Biswanath%20Das.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20had%20arranged%20for%20school%20children%20to%20come%20to%20the%20Beraboi%20fair%20in%20large%20numbers.%20Not%20just%20men%2C%20but%20many%20women%20had%20also%20assembled%20to%20witness%20the%20grand%20exhibition%20featuring%20cow%20welfare%2C%20oil%20pressing%2C%20leather%20book%20binding%2C%20and%20horn%20crafts%2C%20among%20other%20livelihood%20avenues.%20Zamindaars%20and%20rich%20landowners%20rubbed%20shoulders%20with%20sharecroppers%20and%20landless%20labourers.%20Violent%20resistance%20to%20colonial%20rule%20would%20not%20have%20scope%20for%20the%20participation%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20classes%2C%20and%20genders.%20Beraboi%E2%80%99s%20seven-day%20conclave%2C%20from%20March%2025%20to%2031%2C%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Sardar%20Vallabhai%20Patel%2C%20Khan%20Abdul%20Gaffar%20Khan%2C%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20Acharya%20Kripalani%2C%20Jamunalal%20Bajaj%2C%20and%20Maulana%20Azad.%20It%20was%20the%20non-violent%20nature%20of%20the%20event%20that%20allowed%20leaders%20of%20the%20movement%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20public%20rather%20than%20biding%20time%20in%20some%20mountainous%20lair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-and-the-future-of-slow-philosophy%5C%22%3EGandhi%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Slow%20Philosophy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Beraboi%20fair%2C%20local%20vegetables%2C%20milk%2C%20and%20ghee%20were%20used%20in%20cooking%20for%20the%20organisers%20and%20those%20who%20stayed%20for%20more%20than%20a%20day.%C2%A0%20This%20decision%20aligned%20with%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20unceasing%20advocacy%20for%20an%20ethical%20relationship%20between%20producers%20and%20consumers.%20Gandhi%20envisaged%20a%20far%20more%20meaningful%20economic%20system%20wherein%20all%20that%20is%20produced%20is%20largely%20consumed%20within%20the%20same%20locality.%C2%A0%20Today%2C%20this%20concept%20has%20been%20tinkered%20with%20and%20remarketed%20as%20farm-to-table.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Beraboi%20event%20strikes%20one%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20parlance%2C%20as%20fiscally%20prudent.%20It%20also%20relied%20on%20minimum%20support%20from%20the%20state.%20This%20was%20a%20ticketed%20event%20that%20cost%20each%20attendee%202%20paise.%20Overall%2C%2075%2C000%20people%20thronged%20the%20fair%20over%20seven%20days.%20After%20expenses%20on%20the%20food%20and%20accommodation%20for%20thousands%20of%20visitors%2C%20the%20organising%20committee%20was%20left%20with%20a%20balance%20of%20Rs%202%2C000.%20While%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20the%20revenue%20was%20generated%20from%20ticket%20sales%2C%20%3Cem%3Echandaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(subscriptions)%20was%20also%20collected%20from%20attending%20Seva%20Sangh%20members.%20The%20Orissa%20government%20extended%20financial%20support%20only%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20a%20comparatively%20lighter%20burden%20on%20a%20poor%20and%20newly%20formed%20province%20under%20the%20Empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Beraboi%20gathering%20was%20perhaps%20one%20out%20of%20many%20projects%20that%20were%20only%20possible%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20non-violent%20ecosystem.%20And%20all%20these%20were%20not%20faddish%2C%20antiquarian%20projects%20that%20were%20engaged%20in%20a%20quest%20to%20retrieve%20the%20past.%20Non-violence%20created%20here%20the%20space%20to%20accommodate%20modernity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20allowed%20the%20scientist%20Satish%20Chandra%20Das%20Gupta%20to%20work%20within%20the%20movement%20and%20conduct%20experiments%20on%20low-cost%20spinning%20wheels.%20His%20research%20in%20chemistry%20also%20led%20to%20the%20invention%20of%20the%20iconic%20Swadeshi%20Fountain%20Pen%20Ink%2C%20later%20named%20Sulekha%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20Fountain%20pens%20used%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailypioneer.com%2F2023%2Fcolumnists%2Fwhen----sulekha----inked-freedom.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailypioneer.com%2F2023%2Fcolumnists%2Fwhen----sulekha----inked-freedom.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696302946134000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0t1K4rllJKKylntfxLQ2lT%5C%22%3Eexpensive%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0commodities%20because%20they%20were%20imported%20from%20Europe.%20Under%20the%20Gandhian%20non-violent%20vision%2C%20Das%20Gupta%20could%20develop%20useful%20and%20relevant%20indigenous%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHistory%20shows%20that%20violence%20is%20also%20exploitative%20and%20parasitic.%20Both%20sides%20in%20a%20conflict%20engage%20in%20it%2C%20appealing%20to%20a%20higher%20cause.%20Even%20the%20resistor%2C%20who%20resorts%20to%20violence%20against%20the%20oppressor%2C%20demands%20others%20support%20him%20unquestioningly%20with%20their%20resources.%20In%20Beraboi%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20we%20see%20the%20resistors%20generating%20resources%2C%20livelihood%2C%20jobs%2C%20and%20means%20of%20survival%20for%20the%20masses.%20This%20spirit%20also%20drove%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20American%20disciple%2C%20Satyanand%20Stokes%2C%20born%20Samuel%20Evans%2C%20to%20organise%20and%20scale%20up%20apple%20cultivation%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20an%20industry%20that%20has%20to%20this%20day%20sustained%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economy%20as%20well%20as%20its%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20non-violence%20was%20thus%20not%20just%20an%20absence%20of%20violence.%20It%20symbolised%20certain%20kinds%20of%20freedom%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20means%20to%20an%20end.%20He%20used%20non-violence%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20revolutions%20need%20not%20be%20destructive%2C%20sinister%2C%20and%20traumatic%20for%20the%20millions%20that%20are%20sucked%20into%20them.%20From%20ink%20to%20apples%2C%20and%20from%20village%20crafts%20to%20exhibitions%2C%20thousands%20of%20fingers%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20triggers%20and%20assembling%20explosives%2C%20created%20a%20world%20that%20empowered%20the%20impoverished%20masses%20in%20subtle%20but%20significant%20ways.%20The%20conditions%20generated%20under%20non-violence%20were%20used%20by%20Gandhi%20to%20conduct%20experiments%20in%20which%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20nation%20was%20shaped%20and%20tested%20in%20miniature%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFactual%20details%20on%20the%20Beraboi%20exhibition%20have%20been%20taken%20from%20the%20Odia%20translation%20of%20a%20report%20titled%3C%2Fem%3E%20Seven%20days%20of%20Gandhi%20Sewa%20Sangh%20in%20Delang%3Cem%3E%2C%20originally%20in%20Hindi%20and%20published%20in%20Wardha%20in%201938.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESampad%20Patnaik%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist.%20Jatindra%20Nayak%20is%20a%20translator%20and%20academic.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696219092000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30124718%2FIMG_1738.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-jayanti-odisha-beraboi-exhibition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20non-violence%20was%20thus%20not%20just%20an%20absence%20of%20violence.%20It%20symbolised%20certain%20kinds%20of%20freedom%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20means%20to%20an%20end.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-jayanti-odisha-beraboi-exhibition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22