%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1708304499717369955%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20coalition%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20(PPM)-People%E2%80%99s%20National%20Congress%20(PNC)%20led%20a%20successful%20campaign%20which%20focussed%20on%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20specifically%20alleging%20that%20his%20government%20had%20allowed%20the%20Indian%20military%20to%20be%20stationed%20in%20the%20island%20nation.%20The%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%20government%20had%20dismissed%20that%20there%20were%20no%20Indian%20military%20activities%20on%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20the%20campaign%20and%20the%20earlier%20%E2%80%98India%20out%E2%80%99%20slogan%20from%20the%20PPM-PNC%20coalition%2C%20Muizzu%20had%20been%20perceived%20to%20be%20close%20to%20China%2C%20just%20as%20PPM%20leader%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20strongly%20aligned%20with%20Beijing.%20India%20had%20a%20rocky%20relationship%20with%20the%20Maldives%20during%20the%20five%20years%20of%20the%20Yameen%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PPM%E2%80%99s%20vice%20president%20Mohamed%20Shareef%20%E2%80%98Mundhu%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20former%20Maldivian%20ambassador%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Japan%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20India%20should%20be%20worried%20that%20the%20new%20government%20would%20be%20hostile%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20fear-mongering%20about%20China%20is%20unwarranted%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shareef%2C%20a%20former%20PPM%20secretary%20general.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strongly%20value%20and%20want%20to%20work%20with%20India%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20in%20which%20we%20have%20said%20that%20the%20biggest%20stakeholder%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ee%20on%20the%20phone%20from%20Mal%C3%A9.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20there%20were%20sounds%20of%20celebrations%20after%20local%20media%20had%20called%20the%20elections%20in%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20favour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01191615%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-7.15.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01191615%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-7.15.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201072w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01191615%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-7.15.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x189.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01191615%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-7.15.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x645.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677828%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMohamed%20Shareef%20%E2%80%98Mundhu%E2%80%99%20with%20Mohamed%20Muizzu.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2Fmundhu.shareef%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20seas%20that%20any%20non-Indian%20ocean%20states%20have%20a%20stake%20or%20should%20have%20a%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserted%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Maldives%20will%20%E2%80%9Ccontinue%20to%20be%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20strongest%20ally%20in%20the%20international%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20first%20foreign%20trip%20by%20a%20new%20Maldives%20president%20has%20been%20to%20neighbouring%20India.%20%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20continue%20that%20tradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20that%20is%20still%20to%20be%20negotiated%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20incoming%20administration%20will%20also%20assess%20the%20various%20development%20initiatives%20initiated%20by%20India%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20as%20pledged%20by%20Muizzu%20during%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20projects%2C%20we%20will%20honour%20all%20projects.%20But%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20see%20the%20fine%20print%20of%20any%20of%20them.%20Unfortunately%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20share%20any%20of%20the%20agreements%20with%20India%20either%20with%20the%20media%20or%20parliament%E2%80%A6%20We%20would%2C%20of%20course%2C%20be%20reviewing%20it%20and%20if%20the%20agreements%20conform%20to%20our%20constitution%2C%20laws%20and%20they%20are%20feasible%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20naturally%20and%20we%20will%20strongly%20support%20the%20completion%20of%20all%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shareef.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20highlighted%20that%20a%20potential%20obstacle%20in%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20could%20revolve%20around%20the%20matter%20of%20helicopters%20donated%20by%20India%20to%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202018%2C%20President%20Yameen%20asked%20India%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaldivesindependent.com%2Fpolitics%2Fmaldives-gives-india-deadline-to-take-back-gifted-choppers-138674%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithdraw%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20helicopters%20along%20with%20their%20Indian%20crew.%20Following%20the%202018%20presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20opposition%20raised%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaldivesindependent.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdefence-minister-apologises-for-indian-occupation-remarks-144002%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econcerns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20asserting%20that%20this%20arrangement%20served%20as%20a%20covert%20means%20for%20the%20Indian%20military%20to%20establish%20a%20presence%20in%20the%20Maldives%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20that%20the%20Solih%20administration%20firmly%20refuted%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20will%20be%20our%20nearest%20and%20dearest%20neighbour.%20However%2C%20we%20have%20continuously%20been%20making%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20media%20and%20also%20during%20the%20campaign%20that%20we%20cannot%20agree%20to%20have%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20from%20any%20country%2C%20not%20just%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shareef.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stated%20that%20the%20critical%20issue%20with%20the%20agreement%20was%20that%20helicopters%20were%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Maldivian%20military%20after%20local%20pilots%20were%20trained%2C%20but%20Indian%20pilots%20continued%20to%20operate%20the%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F18092755%2Fdownload-1-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F18092755%2Fdownload-1-1.jpeg%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F18092755%2Fdownload-1-1-300x134.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-587488%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22348%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMaldives%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20shake%20hands%20ahead%20of%20their%20meeting%20at%20Hyderabad%20House%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20India%2C%20December%2017%2C%202018.%20Photo%3A%20Reuters%2FAdnan%20Abidi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20want%20to%20discuss%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20transfer%20the%20helicopters%20to%20our%20military%20and%20not%20have%20any%20military%20presence%20..%20that%20is%20the%20one%20issue%20which%20is%20a%20sticking%20point%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Maldivian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shareef.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaldives%E2%80%99%20ambassador%20to%20India%20during%20the%20Yameen%20government%2C%20Ahmed%20Mohamed%20had%20the%20difficult%20job%20of%20keeping%20diplomatic%20ties%20at%20an%20even%20keel%20when%20New%20Delhi%20perceived%20that%20Mal%C3%A9%20had%20gone%20too%20far%20into%20China%E2%80%99s%20orbit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20the%20new%20government%20will%20have%20to%20fulfil%20its%20campaign%20pledges%20related%20to%20Indian%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20cordial%20relations%20with%20India%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20with%20any%20country%20without%20the%20need%20to%20have%20boots%20on%20the%20ground.%20In%20the%20past%20we%20have%20experienced%20Indian%20assistance%20and%20help%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%201988%20November%203rd%20incident%2C%20but%20without%20the%20need%20to%20continue%20Indian%20military%20presence%20indefinitely%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohamed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Solih%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202018%2C%20there%20had%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%2C%20especially%20by%20former%20president%20Mohamed%20Nasheed%2C%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-52743072%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereviewing%20Chinese%20projects%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98debt%20trap%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20there%20had%20been%20no%20such%20public%20China-bashing%20from%20the%20Solih%20government%20and%20no%20Chinese%20projects%20were%20ever%20cancelled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Solih%20government%20did%20shelve%20or%20went%20slow%20on%20some%20Chinese%20projects%20that%20had%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fexpert-speak%2Fchinas-sustained-influence-in-the-maldives%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elike%20the%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20China%20and%20also%20construction%20of%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fin-relief-to-india-maldives-may-scrap-ocean-deal-with-china%2Farticleshow%2F69818016.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eocean%20observatory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20near%20a%20strategically%20located%20island.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShareef%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20Yameen%20government%20had%20only%20done%20commercial%20deals%20with%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20which%20had%20no%20military%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20continue%20to%20say%20over%20the%20five%20years%20and%20we%20challenged%20the%20government%20to%20present%20even%20one%20shred%20of%20evidence%2C%20whether%20we%20had%20any%20untoward%20arrangement%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20which%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20find.%20Because%20our%20arrangement%20with%20China%20at%20that%20time%20was%20entirely%20commercial%20and%20there%20was%20no%20military%20angle%20to%20it%20whatsoever%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20a%20query%2C%20the%20senior%20PPM%20leader%20admitted%20that%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20contacts%20with%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Maldives%20had%20been%20limited%20in%20recent%20times.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20had%20%E2%80%9Cbeen%20in%20touch%20a%20few%20years%20ago%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20there%20has%20not%20been%20much%20contact%20%E2%80%9Cperhaps%20due%20to%20the%20campaigns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20regretted%20that%20India%20had%20begun%20to%20be%20seen%20%E2%80%9Cas%20the%20ally%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20rather%20than%20as%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20former%20Maldivian%20foreign%20minister%20Ahmed%20Shaheed%2C%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20MDP%20supporter%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20China%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20put%20all%20their%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket%20in%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20Nasheed%20was%20bashing%20China%20hard%20five-six%20years%20ago%2C%20Chinese%20diplomats%20were%20reaching%20out%20to%20MDP%20and%20taking%20them%20to%20Beijing%20and%20talking%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shaheed%2C%20who%20had%20been%20foreign%20minister%20between%202005%20and%202010.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Human%20Rights%20Law%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Essex.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20confident%20that%20there%20would%20not%20be%20any%20substantial%20change%20in%20foreign%20policy%20direction%20for%20Maldives%20after%20the%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20going%20to%20kick%20India%20out.%20But%20what%20they%20are%20saying%20is%20let%E2%80%99s%20have%20more%20transparency.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20make%20sure%20that%20it%20(agreements)%20serves%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20interest.%20They%20do%20serve%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20interests%20but%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shaheed%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20Solih%20government%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9Cover-secrecy%20and%20over-securitisation%20of%20everything%20Indian%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20(Solih)%20government%20also%20wanted%20to%20close%20all%20access%20to%20India%20for%20the%20people%20to%20serve%20their%20own%20agenda.%20India%20was%20played%20out%20by%20this%20government%20by%20not%20letting%20India%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20neutral%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDaniel%20Bosley%2C%20a%20British%20journalist%20who%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDescent-into-Paradise-Journalists-Maldives%2Fdp%2F9389109817%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20a%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20based%20on%20his%20political%20reporting%20in%20the%20Maldives%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20while%20PPM%20coalition%20%E2%80%9Ccaptured%20headlines%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20many%20Maldivians%20feel%20an%20intrusive%20Indian%20military%20presence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20termed%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Clazy%20populism%20by%20an%20opposition%20that%20has%20no%20democratic%20vision%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20nation%20will%20pivot%20back%20towards%20China%20now%2C%20though%20it%20finds%20itself%20deeply%20indebted%20to%20both%20superpowers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBosley%2C%20who%20had%20been%20editor%20of%20the%20Minivan%20News%20(later%20known%20as%20Maldives%20Independent)%2C%20criticised%20the%20MDP%20for%20having%20squandered%20%E2%80%9Can%20incredible%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20to%20push%20the%20democratic%20transition%20forward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20elected%20to%20stem%20the%20rampant%20corruption%20and%20extremist%20violence%20that%20was%20taking%20hold%20under%20the%20previous%20government.%20But%20progress%20on%20these%20fronts%20has%20stalled%20and%20the%20party%20has%20descended%20into%20farcical%20in-fighting.%E2%80%9D%20The%20MDP%E2%80%99s%20split%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%20defeat%20with%20Nasheed%E2%80%99s%20breakaway%20faction%20polling%20a%20respectable%20third%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20the%20presidential%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20felt%20that%20the%20general%20populace%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20much%20difference%20between%20the%20Solih%20and%20Yameen%20administrations%2C%20%E2%80%9Csave%20for%20a%20little%20less%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20fear%20this%20may%20be%20the%20first%20change%20we%20see%2C%20with%20dangerous%20terrorists%20%E2%80%93%20some%20charged%20with%20murdering%20my%20former%20colleague%2C%20Ahmed%20Rilwan%20%E2%80%93%20likely%20to%20return%20to%20the%20streets%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Bosley.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20developments%20a%20day%20after%20the%20election%20results%20was%20the%20transfer%20of%20former%20president%20Yameen%2C%20who%20is%20serving%20a%20sentence%20of%2011%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F85035%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20house%20arrest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBosley%20pointed%20out%20this%20left%20president-elect%20Muizzu%20in%20precisely%20the%20same%20situation%20President%20Solih%20found%20himself%20in%20five%20years%20ago%20when%20former%20President%20Nasheed%20returned%20from%20exile%20and%20was%20exonerated.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20this%20election%20shows%2C%20the%20result%20was%20disastrous%20bickering.%20Yameen%20was%20unhappy%20that%20his%20party%20contested%20the%20election%20without%20him%20as%20the%20candidate%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20infamously%20comfortable%20wielding%20influence%20from%20the%20shadows.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdmitting%20that%20future%20tensions%20between%20Muizzu%20and%20Yameen%20are%20inevitable%2C%20Shaheed%2C%20however%2C%20contended%20that%20both%20possessed%20a%20pragmatic%20outlook%2C%20which%20should%20prevent%20their%20personal%20dynamics%20from%20destabilizing%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CMuizzu%20is%20a%20very%20pragmatic%20person.%20His%20pragmatism%20would%20mean%20that%20he%20would%20want%20survival%2C%20goodwill%20and%20not%20drama%E2%80%A6%20Yameen%20is%20pragmatic%20enough%20to%20know%20that%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20sink%20his%20own%20ship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696168058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01175213%2FF7Wa7ZlacAAu3nj.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-biggest-stakeholder-indian-ocean-region-advisor-muizzu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohamed%20Muizzu%20as%20the%20next%20Maldives%20president%20has%20led%20to%20apprehension%20about%20relations%20with%20its%20largest%20neighbour.%20However%2C%20his%20advisor%20Mohamed%20Shareef%20%E2%80%98Mundhu%E2%80%99%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20India%20should%20be%20worried%20that%20the%20new%20government%20would%20be%20hostile%20to%20New%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-biggest-stakeholder-indian-ocean-region-advisor-muizzu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Europe%20wins%20back%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696167300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-ryder-cup-europe_6305548.jpg%3F20231001210837%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fryder-cup-europe-wins-back-trophy-after-acrimonious-tournament-ends-in-rome-12974264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Europe's%20golfers%20have%20won%20back%20the%20Ryder%20Cup%20from%20the%20USA%20after%20an%20event-packed%20tournament%20in%20Rome.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2044%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fryder-cup-europe-wins-back-trophy-after-acrimonious-tournament-ends-in-rome-12974264%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fryder-cup-europe-wins-back-trophy-after-acrimonious-tournament-ends-in-rome-12974264%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fryder-cup-europe-wins-back-trophy-after-acrimonious-tournament-ends-in-rome-12974264%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Slow%20Philosophy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%20M.K.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20work%20have%20attracted%20critical%20scrutiny%20and%20inspired%20socio-political%20movements%20across%20the%20globe.%20His%20political%20and%20social%20visions%20have%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20much%20controversy%2C%20provoking%20both%20admiration%20and%20criticism.%20Even%20though%20he%20saw%20himself%20as%20an%20ordinary%20political%20worker%2C%20his%20expansive%20writings%20on%20various%20subjects%20have%20become%20rich%20resources%20for%20scholarly%20reflections%20on%20a%20number%20of%20political%2C%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20environmental%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20importance%20to%20political%2C%20religious%20and%20social%20transformations%20in%20the%20past%20century%2C%20scholars%20have%20rarely%20taken%20him%20seriously%20as%20a%20philosopher%20whose%20teachings%20transcend%20both%20his%20time%2C%20nationalist%20political%20struggles%2C%20and%20his%20religious%20doctrines.%20Read%20as%20a%20slow%20philosopher%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20much%20to%20offer%20to%20illuminate%20contemporary%20questions%20of%20human%20existence%20and%20struggles%20for%20meaning%20in%20our%20time.%20What%20kind%20of%20a%20philosophic%20figure%20does%20Gandhi%20make%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20historian%20and%20philosopher%20Pierre%20Hadot%2C%20in%20his%20landmark%20book%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPhilosophy%20as%20a%20Way%20of%20Life%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20divides%20the%20history%20of%20Western%20philosophy%20into%20two%20traditions%20%E2%80%93%20philosophy%20as%20a%20discourse%20and%20philosophy%20as%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20The%20first%20%E2%80%93%20philosophy%20as%20production%20of%20discourse%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20dominant%20tradition%20with%20its%20interest%20in%20producing%20novel%20concepts%20and%20theories%20more%20like%20a%20domain%20of%20science.%20This%20is%20the%20tradition%20that%20came%20to%20define%20what%20is%20taken%20to%20be%20philosophy%20in%20the%20contemporary%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP's%20Gandhi%20Dilemma%3A%20How%20To%20Use%20the%20%E2%80%98Brand%E2%80%99%20While%20Destroying%20Its%20Spirit%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-gandhi-dilemma-brand-spirit%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Dilemma%3A%20How%20To%20Use%20the%20%E2%80%98Brand%E2%80%99%20While%20Destroying%20Its%20Spirit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20tradition%2C%20however%2C%20has%20its%20concern%20both%20in%20the%20production%20of%20philosophical%20wisdom%20and%20exemplary%20philosophical%20life%20through%20what%20Hadot%20called%20%E2%80%98spiritual%20exercises%E2%80%99.%20Philosophy%20as%20a%20way%20of%20life%20is%20primarily%20focused%20on%20training%20the%20student%20of%20philosophy%20in%20the%20arts%20of%20dialogue%2C%20self-examination%2C%20self-transformation%2C%20attention%2C%20inquiry%2C%20slow%20and%20reflective%20meditation%2C%20reading%2C%20writing%2C%20relating%20to%20others%20and%20otherness%20in%20the%20world%2C%20ethical%20orientation%2C%20searching%20after%20truth%2C%20arts%20of%20public%20confession%2C%20and%20striving%20for%20human%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20tradition%2C%20philosophical%20texts%20become%20training%20grounds%2C%20not%20sources%20of%20new%20knowledge.%20They%20are%20formative%2C%20not%20informative.%20The%20discourses%20of%20the%20past%20philosophers%20act%20more%20like%20reminders%20of%20something%20the%20reader%20already%20knew%20but%20for%20some%20reason%20has%20forgotten.%20The%20object%20is%20the%20production%20of%20philosophical%20life%20and%20a%20figure%20of%20a%20philosopher%20exemplifying%20an%20image%20of%20possibilities%20of%20human%20excellence.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20transform%20oneself%20through%20slow%2C%20laborious%20and%20even%20painful%20spiritual%20exercises%20involving%20both%20the%20body%20and%20mind%20so%20as%20to%20acquire%20a%20new%20orientation%20and%20reformation%20of%20unhelpful%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHadot%E2%80%99s%20framework%20helps%20recast%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20work%20in%20a%20new%20light.%20Throughout%20his%20life%2C%20Gandhi%20insisted%20on%20experimenting%20on%20himself%20much%20like%20philosophers%20in%20the%20tradition%20of%20philosophy%20as%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20He%20believed%20that%20one%20should%20first%20change%20oneself%20if%20one%20aspires%20to%20change%20others.%20It%20is%20this%20impulse%20and%20principle%20that%20finds%20its%20best%20expression%20in%20the%20title%20of%20his%20autobiography%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMy%20Experiments%20with%20Truth.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20writings%20exemplify%20the%20spirit%20of%20dialogue%20both%20in%20form%20and%20content.%20A%20dialogical%20form%20of%20communication%20and%20engagement%20demands%20as%20its%20primary%20condition%20that%20the%20speaker%20is%20trustworthy%20and%20is%20able%20to%20establish%20quick%20trust%20with%20his%20interlocutors.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20with%20others%20was%20not%20always%20successful%3B%20his%20best-known%20failure%20was%20his%20exchanges%20with%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%20That%20does%20not%20detract%20from%20his%20legacy%20of%20writing%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20opens%20minds%20rather%20than%20shuts%20them%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20writings%20are%20carefully%20crafted%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20of%20mind%20rather%20than%20win%20an%20argument.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20is%20adept%20at%20a%20philosophical%20style%20that%20draws%20the%20reader%20to%20the%20completion%20of%20his%20texts%20rather%20than%20logical%20exposition.%20Gandhi%20insisted%20that%20he%20was%20searching%20for%20the%20truth%20without%20having%20found%20one.%20He%20wrote%20often%20that%20given%20the%20limitations%20of%20human%20understanding%2C%20any%20claim%20to%20infallibility%20would%20be%20dangerous%20and%20dogmatic.%20Even%20though%20he%20was%20a%20man%20of%20faith%2C%20he%20never%20was%20dogmatic%2C%20much%20like%20Dutch%20philosopher%20S%C3%B8ren%20Kierkegaard%20who%20insisted%20that%20faith%20rests%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20into%20the%20unknown.%20As%20German-American%20political%20theorist%20Hannah%20Arendt%20wrote%2C%20one%20can%20be%20truthful%20without%20knowing%20the%20Truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Plot%20to%20Kill%20Gandhi%20Was%20a%20Manifestation%20of%20a%20Battle%20for%20the%20Soul%20of%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-plot-to-kill-gandhi-was-a-manifestation-of-a-battle-for-the-soul-of-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Plot%20to%20Kill%20Gandhi%20Was%20a%20Manifestation%20of%20a%20Battle%20for%20the%20Soul%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20writings%2C%20much%20like%20the%20Socratic%20dialogues%2C%20are%20intended%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20of%20attitude%20in%20the%20reader.%20They%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20read%20slowly%20so%20as%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20in%20the%20orientation%20of%20the%20reader.%20Gandhi%20wrote%20not%20only%20to%20inform%20but%20to%20transform%20the%20reader.%20In%20the%20journals%20he%20published%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20Gandhi%20would%20insist%20that%20the%20readers%20take%20time%2C%20collect%20the%20articles%20they%20read%2C%20and%20re-read%20them%20often%20until%20they%20not%20only%20have%20absorbed%20the%20contents%20but%20the%20spirit%20underlying%20the%20mode%20of%20communication.%20Much%20like%20St.%20Augustine%2C%20Gandhi%20took%20seriously%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20genuine%20reformer%20should%20become%20a%20skillful%20public%20confessor%20%E2%80%93%20philosophy%20as%20a%20public%20confession.%20This%20is%20very%20demanding%20for%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20difficult%20than%20to%20be%20truthful%20to%20oneself.%20Public%20confessions%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20seen%20as%20inauthentic%20and%20hypocritical.%20Gandhi%20showed%20great%20mastery%20in%20this%20art.%20%3Cem%3EMy%20Experiments%20with%20Truth%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20exhaustive%20demonstration%20both%20of%20the%20necessity%20of%20this%20art%20and%20a%20skillful%20way%20to%20do%20it%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20has%20been%20noted%20by%20many%20scholars%2C%20reading%20widely%2C%20slowly%20and%20equally%20selectively%20has%20been%20crucial%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20worldview%20and%20life%20orientation.%20He%20took%20inspiration%20from%20religious%20texts%20such%20as%20the%20Gita%2C%20Bible%2C%20Koran%2C%20and%20other%20religious%20and%20philosophical%20texts%2C%20often%20retranslating%20them%20to%20serve%20his%20ethical%20project.%20His%20acts%20of%20translation%20are%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20rewriting%2C%20and%20appropriating%20rather%20than%20fidelity%20to%20the%20literal.%20Arguably%2C%20his%20translation%20of%20the%20Gita%2C%20for%20example%2C%20takes%20its%20cues%20from%20Tolstoy%E2%80%99s%20reworking%20of%C2%A0the%20%3Cem%3EGospels%20in%20Brief%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20inventive%2C%20accessible%2C%20and%20creative%20appropriation%2C%20yet%20true%20to%20the%20underlying%20original%20message.%20This%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20originality%20and%20ingenuity%20few%20thinkers%20in%20history%20could%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%2C%20like%20the%20philosophers%20in%20the%20tradition%2C%20placed%20great%20significance%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20searcher%20after%20truth%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20die%20for%20his%20idea.%20The%20willingness%20to%20die%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20belief%20marks%20Socrates%2C%20Jesus%2C%20Buddha%2C%20and%20others.%20The%20true%20mark%20of%20a%20genius%20seeking%20to%20transform%20the%20world%20is%20not%20their%20cleverness%20but%20their%20commitment%2C%20a%20commitment%20that%20might%20call%20upon%20them%20one%20day%20to%20make%20the%20ultimate%20sacrifice.%20Gandhi%20lived%20and%20ultimately%20died%20for%20his%20truth%20much%20like%20Socrates%2C%20making%20his%20life%20both%20memorable%20and%20tragic.%20The%20manner%20of%20his%20death%2C%20as%20much%20as%20his%20life%2C%20committed%20to%20the%20search%20for%20truth%20in%20the%20darkest%20corners%20of%20humanity%2C%20in%20itself%2C%20marks%20him%20as%20an%20untimely%20figure%20who%20will%20continue%20to%20shape%20human%20expectations%20and%20the%20quest%20for%20human%20excellence%20far%20longer%20like%20the%20figure%20of%20Socrates%20that%20he%20admired%20as%20a%20soldier%20of%20truth.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20arts%20of%20slow%20thinking%20and%20slow%20living%20will%20continue%20to%20instruct%20and%20inform%20us%20in%20our%20search%20for%20a%20counter-tradition%20and%20corrective%20force%20in%20an%20age%20marked%20by%20speed%20and%20haste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EV.%20Krishnappa%20is%20Professor%20and%20Executive%20Director%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Centre%20for%20Contemporary%20Ethics%20at%20RV%20University%2C%20Bengaluru.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20solely%20those%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696167017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-and-the-future-of-slow-philosophy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20writings%2C%20much%20like%20the%20Socratic%20dialogues%2C%20are%20intended%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20of%20attitude%20in%20the%20reader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-and-the-future-of-slow-philosophy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prices%20of%20Commercial%20LPG%2C%20Domestic%20Natural%20Gas%2C%20Jet%20Fuel%20Up%3B%20Bound%20To%20Raise%20Inflation%20and%20Hit%20Consumers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01171739%2Fpexels-pixabay-266896.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Public%20sector%20oil%20and%20gas%20company%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiocl.com%2Fpetrol-diesel-price%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Oil%20Corporation%20Limited%20has%20hiked%20the%20prices%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20commercial%20LPG%20or%20Liquified%20Petroleum%20Gas.%20The%20price%20has%20been%20increased%20by%20Rs%20209%20per%20cylinder%2C%20with%20the%20new%20prices%20coming%20into%20effect%20on%20Sunday%2C%20October%201.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20change%20yet%20in%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20LPG.%20The%20government%20reduced%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20by%20Rs%20200%20on%20August%2029%2C%20projecting%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Rakhi%20gift%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20move%20instead%20drew%20attention%20to%20how%20high%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20was%20and%20how%20the%20Rs%20200%20cut%20was%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20increase%20since%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20retail%20price%20of%2019%20kg%20commercial%20LPG%20cylinders%20in%20Delhi%20will%20now%20be%20Rs%201731.50%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fcommercial-lpg-prices-hiked-by-rs-209-per-cylinder-11458621.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EMoneycontrol%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Fcommercial-lpg-prices-hiked-by-over-200%2Farticle67368509.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Chennai%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20new%20price%20is%20Rs%201%2C898%2Fcylinder.%20It%20was%20Rs%201%2C685%20per%20cylinder%20in%20September.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELPG%20is%20used%20for%20cooking%2C%20as%20motor%20fuel%2C%20and%20for%20heating%20as%20well%20as%20cooling%20(refrigeration)%20purposes%20and%20in%20certain%20industries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20bound%20to%20impact%20inflation%20rates%20as%20the%20increased%20cost%20is%20shifted%20to%20consumers%20and%20if%20connected%20with%20items%20of%20necessary%20consumption%2C%20it%20hurts%20the%20pockets%20of%20all%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20art%20of%20framing.%F0%9F%91%8C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlzhqtWzxsY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FlzhqtWzxsY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Karthik%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40beastoftraal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbeastoftraal%2Fstatus%2F1708432269692801086%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20persistent%20complaint%20that%20during%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20even%20though%20international%20crude%20prices%20have%20been%20low%2C%20the%20fuel%20prices%20were%20still%20high%20for%20consumers%20%E2%80%93%20with%20excise%20duties%20and%20cess%20helping%20the%20revenues%20of%20the%20government%20(mostly%20the%20Centre).%20Now%2C%20citing%20rising%20international%20prices%2C%20the%20price%20rise%20is%20still%20passed%20on%20to%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDomestic%20natural%20gas%20prices%20also%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20price%20of%20domestic%20natural%20gas%20has%20also%20been%20raised%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20From%20%248.60%20per%20metric%20million%20British%20thermal%20unit%20(mmBtu)%2C%20it%20will%20now%20go%20up%20to%20%249.20%20per%20mmBtu%2C%20according%20to%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Petroleum%20and%20Natural%20Gas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20happened%20for%20the%20second%20month%20in%20a%20row.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20per%20mmBtu%20price%20was%20increased%20from%20%247.85%20to%20%248.60.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20the%20four%20big%20gas%20trading%20hubs%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20Henry%20Hub%2C%20Albany%2C%20National%20Balancing%20Point%20(UK)%20and%20Russian%20gas%20used%20to%20decide%20what%20the%20domestic%20gas%20price%20would%20be.%20This%20was%20fixed%20for%20six%20months%20in%20one%20go.%20As%20per%20the%20new%20formula%20adopted%20by%20the%20government%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcentre-hikes-domestic-natural-gas-prices-from-today-what-does-it-mean-for-common-man-101696121792216.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecited%20by%3Cem%3E%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20natural%20gas%20is%20now%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20price%20of%20the%20Indian%20crude%20basket%20every%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJet%20fuel%20up%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20price%20of%20jet%20fuel%20or%20Aviation%20Turbine%20Fuel%20(ATF)%20was%20also%20hiked%20by%205%25.%20ATF%2C%20for%20domestic%20airlines%2C%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Chiked%20by%205%25%20to%20highest%20this%20year%2C%20and%20may%20push%20up%20airfares%20in%20the%20festive%20season%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fatf-price-hike-commercial-lpg-8963607%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20prices%20have%20been%20going%20up%20and%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fourth%20straight%20monthly%20increase%20since%20July.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELPG%20blues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Ujjwala%20scheme%2C%20centred%20around%20affordable%20LPG%20for%20women%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20enable%20a%20transition%20from%20smoke-fired%20%3Cem%3Echullahs%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20well%20as%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20women%20to%20cook%20at%20affordable%20prices.%20But%20jittery%20after%20the%20comprehensive%20electoral%20loss%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20in%20some%20part%20due%20to%20anger%20over%20rising%20LPG%20prices%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flpg-price-cut-modis-rakhi-gift-ends-up-drawing-attention-to-inflation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20reported%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20earlier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20rushed%20%E2%80%9Cto%20salvage%20its%20flagship%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20Scheme%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20reducing%20prices.%20The%20Rs%20200%20reduction%2C%20critics%20pointed%20out%2C%20was%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20price%20increase%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20slashed%20subsidies%20on%20LPG%20to%20one-sixth%20since%202018-19.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20the%20board%2C%20the%20revised%20fuel%20price%20rises%20kicked%20into%20effect%20on%20Sunday%2C%20when%20inflation%20has%20been%20consistently%20well%20above%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20acceptable%20bandwidth%20of%202-6%25%2C%20greatly%20adding%20to%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2FEconomy%2Fcommercial-lpg-prices-hiked-by-over-200%2Farticle67368509.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESelwin%2C%20an%20autorickshaw%20driver%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20hike%20was%20%E2%80%9Cuncalled%20for%E2%80%9D%20amidst%20rising%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20unable%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Already%20CNG%20and%20petrol%20prices%20are%20quite%20high%20making%20LPG%20a%20better%20alternative%20due%20to%20its%20pricing.%20But%20if%20prices%20keep%20increasing%20then%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20viable%20to%20be%20in%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696161654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01171739%2Fpexels-pixabay-266896.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fcommercial-lpg-domestic-natural-gas-jet-fuel-prices-up-inflation-consumers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20August%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20tried%20to%20project%20a%20small%20snip%20in%20domestic%20LPG%20cylinder%20prices%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Rakhi%20gift.%E2%80%99%20Fuel%20price%20hikes%20feed%20the%20inflation%20chain%20and%20heighten%20all-round%20hardship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fcommercial-lpg-domestic-natural-gas-jet-fuel-prices-up-inflation-consumers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20Gandhi%20Dilemma%3A%20How%20To%20Use%20the%20%E2%80%98Brand%E2%80%99%20While%20Destroying%20Its%20Spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F03081624%2FGandhi-Modi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20prepare%20to%20celebrate%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20father%20of%20the%20nation%20on%20October%202%20this%20year%2C%20we%20do%20need%20to%20look%20back%20at%20his%20teachings%20and%20the%20prevailing%20situation%20in%20the%20country.%20His%20global%20recognition%20was%20manifested%20when%20the%20leaders%20from%20different%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Frajghat-pm-modi-welcomes-g20-leaders-pay-tributes-mahatma-gandhi-8932970%2F%5C%22%3Eassembled%20on%20Raj%20Ghat%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20him%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20That%20even%20those%20who%20subscribe%20to%20the%20ideology%20which%20put%20three%20bullets%20into%20his%20chest%20could%20not%20ignore%20him%20was%20more%20than%20obvious.%20While%20the%20ideology%20Gandhi%20propounded%20is%20spreading%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20concepts%20of%20truth%2C%20non-violence%2C%20communal%20harmony%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20formulating%20policies%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98last%20person%E2%80%99%20in%20mind%20in%20India%20today%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20dominant%20ideology%20in%20India%20sees%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%20as%20foreign%20religions.%20This%20understanding%20is%20one%20of%20the%20foundations%20of%20hate%20against%20minorities%20and%20leads%20to%20violence%20against%20them.%20How%20did%20Gandhi%20see%20the%20presence%20of%20different%20religions%20in%20India%3F%20He%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CCertainly%20the%20great%20faiths%20held%20by%20the%20people%20of%20India%20are%20adequate%20for%20her%20people.%E2%80%9D%20He%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20list%20the%20faiths%20of%20India%2C%20%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20Christianity%20and%20Judaism%2C%20Hinduism%20and%20its%20offshoots%2C%20Islam%20and%20Zoroastrianism%20are%20living%20faiths.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prevalent%20dominant%20ideology%20presents%20all%20the%20ills%20of%20Hindu%20society%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20oppression%20of%20Muslim.%20Gandhi%20saw%20history%20in%20a%20totally%20different%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Hindus%20flourished%20under%20Moslem%20sovereigns%20and%20Moslems%20under%20the%20Hindu.%20Each%20party%20recognized%20that%20mutual%20fighting%20was%20suicidal%2C%20and%20that%20neither%20party%20would%20abandon%20its%20religion%20by%20force%20of%20arms.%20Both%20parties%2C%20therefore%2C%20decided%20to%20live%20in%20peace.%20With%20the%20English%20advent%20quarrels%20recommenced%E2%80%A6Is%20the%20God%20of%20the%20Mohammedan%20different%20from%20the%20God%20of%20the%20Hindu%3F%20Religions%20are%20different%20roads%20converging%20to%20the%20same%20point.%20What%20does%20it%20matter%20that%20we%20take%20different%20roads%20so%20long%20as%20we%20reach%20the%20same%20goal%3F%20Wherein%20is%20the%20cause%20of%20quarrelling%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20is%20made%20of%20conversion%20to%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%2C%20scattered%20but%20serious%20anti-Christian%20violence%20is%20ascendant.%20What%20did%20Gandhi%20think%20of%20conversions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Two%20races%20(Hindus%20and%20Muslims)%20lived%20at%20peace%20amongst%20themselves%20during%20Muslim%20rule.%20Let%20it%20be%20remembered%20that%20many%20Hindus%20embraced%20Islam%20before%20the%20advent%20of%20Muslim%20rule%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20my%20belief%20that%20had%20there%20been%20no%20Muslim%20rule%2C%20there%20would%20still%20have%20been%20Musalmans%20in%20India%2C%20even%20as%20there%20would%20have%20been%20Christians%20had%20there%20been%20no%20British%20rule.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Musalmans%20lived%20at%20war%20with%20one%20another%20before%20British%20rule.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20great%20disciple%20Nehru%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Discovery%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20points%20out%20about%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20like%20some%20ancient%20palimpsest%20on%20which%20layer%20upon%20layer%20of%20thought%20and%20reverie%20had%20been%20inscribed%2C%20and%20yet%20no%20succeeding%20layer%20had%20completely%20hidden%20or%20erased%20what%20had%20been%20written%20previously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30160235%2FGandhi-1944-1024x537.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-638277%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22629%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20in%201944.%20Photo%3A%20By%20Unknown%20author%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20Public%20Domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHate%20is%20being%20spread%20against%20Gandhi%20in%20an%20intense%20manner.%20Through%20word%20of%20mouth%20and%20other%20systematic%20channels%2C%20propaganda%20is%20spread%20that%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20prevent%20the%20hanging%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20Gandhi%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fopinion%2Fmahatma-gandhi-did-all-he-could-to-try-and-save-bhagat-singh-from-the-gallows%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fopinion%2Fmahatma-gandhi-did-all-he-could-to-try-and-save-bhagat-singh-from-the-gallows%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696237998274000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw38ag0dTNRaPOryIY_-7LEJ%5C%22%3Etwo%20letters%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Lord%20Irwin%20seeking%20the%20death%20sentence%20to%20be%20commuted%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20or%20seeking%20a%20suspension%20of%20the%20death%20sentence.%20Lord%20Irwin%20was%20considering%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20request%20but%20was%20threatened%20by%20British%20officers%20working%20in%20Punjab%20of%20resignation%20en%20masse.%20One%20should%20recall%20that%20it%20was%20Gandhi%20who%20drafted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Fblog%2Fthis-month-in-constitution-making-march-1931-bhagat-singh-hanged-karachi-resolution-passed%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Fblog%2Fthis-month-in-constitution-making-march-1931-bhagat-singh-hanged-karachi-resolution-passed%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696237998274000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3t1sbgwrXxoux9cSmmtwp4%5C%22%3Eresolution%20in%20the%20Karachi%3C%2Fa%3E%20Congress%20of%201931%2C%20criticising%20the%20government%20for%20Bhagat%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20hanging.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20spread%20the%20lie%20that%20Gandhi%20treated%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20very%20badly.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20though%20there%20were%20differences%20in%20their%20approach%20towards%20non-violence%20and%20driving%20the%20British%20away%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20they%20had%20great%20mutual%20respect.%20Bose%20called%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Father%20of%20the%20Nation%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20named%20the%20first%20battalion%20of%20the%20Azad%20Hind%20Fauz%20(AHF)%20after%20the%20Mahatma.%20Gandhi%20on%20his%20part%20called%20Bose%20a%20%E2%80%98Prince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-today-needs-legacy-of-bose-and-mahatma-sugata-bose%2Farticle2293696.ece%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-today-needs-legacy-of-bose-and-mahatma-sugata-bose%2Farticle2293696.ece%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1696237998274000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3gym67Olcam5lQ1pi2jNMH%5C%22%3Eamongst%20patriots%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20and%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20officers%20of%20the%20AHF%20in%20jail.%20It%20was%20the%20Congress%20which%20fought%20the%20cases%20of%20the%20AHF%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20controversy%20has%20been%20magnified%20about%20differences%20with%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%20While%20Babasaheb%20was%20asking%20for%20separate%20electorates%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20for%20reserved%20constituencies.%20This%20was%20to%20keep%20the%20society%20united%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle.%20Babasaheb%20did%20recognise%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20tallest%20leader%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%20after%20his%20second%20marriage%2C%20an%20inter-caste%20one%2C%20stated%20that%20had%20Gandhi%20been%20alive%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20happy.%20It%20was%20Gandhi%20who%20ensured%20that%20Ambedkar%20was%20part%20of%20the%20first%20cabinet%20of%20India%20and%20also%20suggested%20that%20Ambedkar%20should%20be%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20controversy%20over%20who%20should%20be%20the%20first%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20Sardar%20Patel%20or%20Nehru%2C%20Gandhi%20did%20favour%20the%20latter.%20It%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20Nehru%20and%20Patel%20were%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20two%20closest%20associates.%20He%20favoured%20Nehru%20mostly%20for%20his%20grasp%20of%20global%20politics.%20There%20may%20be%20other%20unstated%20factors%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Nehru%20being%20the%20most%20popular%20leader%20among%20the%20masses%20after%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20as%20the%20younger%20leader%2C%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20nation%20for%20a%20longer%20time.%20These%20are%20just%20guesses%20%E2%80%93%20as%20far%20as%20Patel%20and%20Nehru%20were%20concerned%2C%20they%20were%20totally%20in%20sync%20with%20each%20other%2C%20irrespective%20of%20a%20few%20differences.%20Patel%20said%20of%20Nehru%20that%20he%20was%20not%20only%20his%20younger%20brother%20but%20also%20his%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20scenario%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20reexamine%20the%20dangerous%20path%20of%20hate%20which%20is%20stalking%20the%20streets.%20It%20was%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Ishwar%2C%20Allah%20Tero%20Naam%E2%80%99%20which%20kept%20all%20religious%20communities%20together%20in%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle.%20Following%20his%20message%20of%20social%20reform%2C%20struggle%20against%20the%20caste%20system%2C%20and%20unity%20across%20religious%20lines%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20That%20will%20be%20our%20best%20tribute%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696159746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F03081624%2FGandhi-Modi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-gandhi-dilemma-brand-spirit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20ideology%20Gandhi%20propounded%20is%20spreading%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20concepts%20of%20truth%2C%20non-violence%2C%20communal%20harmony%20in%20India%20today%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-gandhi-dilemma-brand-spirit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey%3A%20%E2%80%98Terrorists%E2%80%99%20Attack%20Interior%20Ministry%20in%20Ankara%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01165304%2FScreensho