va%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20should%20count%20their%20last%20days.%C2%A0Shivaji%20used%20to%20sign%20off%20as%20%E2%80%98Sahishna%20Hindu%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20ironically%20means%20tolerant%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20after%20writer%20Dr%20Vasundhara%20Bhupathi%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Basaveshnagar%20police%20station%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20she%20received%20a%20warning%20letter%20from%20the%20same%20individual%20just%20three%20days%20later.%20The%20letter%20questioned%20her%20decision%20to%20involve%20the%20police%20and%20cautioned%20her%20against%20it%2C%20implying%20it%20was%20an%20unwise%20move%20on%20her%20part.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20not%20told%20anyone%20about%20this%2C%20it%20was%20not%20reported%20in%20the%20media%20either%2C%20but%20still%20this%20person%20got%20the%20information.%20This%20made%20my%20family%20worry%20even%20more%20because%20it%20could%20mean%20that%20either%20I%20was%20being%20tracked%20closely%20or%20even%20that%20someone%20close%20to%20the%20police%20had%20leaked%20the%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20had%20told%20TNM.%20According%20to%20the%20writers%20whom%20TNM%20spoke%20to%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20letter%20always%20coincided%20with%20any%20public%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20writers%20against%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2022%2C%20a%20group%20of%20progressive%20thinkers%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20intellectuals%20met%20with%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah.%20The%20delegation%2C%20led%20by%20prominent%20writers%20K%20Marulasiddappa%20and%20Vasundhara%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20persistent%20threats%20they%20had%20been%20facing%20for%20over%2015%20months.%20Collectively%2C%20they%20lodged%20numerous%20complaints%2C%20with%20seven%20First%20Information%20Reports%20(FIRs)%20being%20filed.%20Despite%20this%2C%20there%20had%20been%20little%20headway%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20the%20threat%20letters%20had%20persisted.%20Following%20the%20meeting%20with%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20the%20first%20since%20the%20Congress%20regained%20power%2C%20the%20government%20entrusted%20the%20investigation%20to%20the%20Central%20Crime%20Branch%20(CCB).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Special%20Wing%20CCB%2C%20and%20experts%20with%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20found%20that%20all%20letters%20were%20written%20by%20the%20same%20person%20but%20were%20posted%20from%20different%20districts%20and%20taluks.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20the%20letters%2C%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20had%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20provide%20suitable%20security%20to%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fbengaluru-police-arrest-man-for-sending-threat-letters-to-writers-in-karnataka%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696158048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01160633%2FScreenshot-2023-10-01-at-4.06.23-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengaluru-police-arrest-man-for-sending-threat-letters-to-writers-in-karnataka%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%2C%20Shivaji%20Rao%2C%20in%20his%20letters%2C%20used%20to%20sign%20off%20as%20%E2%80%98Sahishna%20Hindu%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20ironically%20means%20tolerant%20Hindu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengaluru-police-arrest-man-for-sending-threat-letters-to-writers-in-karnataka%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gross%20GST%20collection%20rises%2010%25%20to%20over%20Rs%201.62%20trillion%20in%20September%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696156966000%2C%22visual%22%