%20breaches%2C%20claiming%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20and%20throwing%20millions%20of%20others%20into%20jeopardy.%20But%20what%20followed%20was%20a%20glorious%20saga%20of%20survival%2C%20where%20people%20literally%20waded%20to%20safer%20shores%20on%20the%20back%20of%20exceptional%20camaraderie.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%3A%20Everyone%20is%20a%20Hero%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20Jude%20Anthany%20Joseph%2C%20selected%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20official%20entry%20to%20the%20Best%20Foreign%20Language%20Film%20category%20at%20the%2096th%20Academy%20Awards%2C%20is%20an%20adept%20filmmaker%E2%80%99s%20take%20on%20what%20Kerala%20went%20through%20those%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20titles%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20with%20sound%20bites%20and%20newspaper%20clippings%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98deluge%20of%20%E2%80%9999%E2%80%99%2C%20harking%20back%20to%20the%20massive%20flood%20of%201924%20(Malayalam%20year%20of%201099).%20A%20TV%20reporter%20is%20heard%20narrating%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Kundala%20Valley%20Railway%20of%20Munnar.%20Environmental%20destruction%2C%20a%20fear%20of%20looming%20catastrophe%2C%20and%20confidence%20in%20modern-era%20alert%20systems%20are%20brought%20up%20before%20the%20fictitious%20village%20of%20Aruvikkulam.%20A%20clever%20play%20of%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98Aruvi%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Kulam%E2%80%99%2C%20meaning%20stream%20and%20pond%20respectively%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20village%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20place%20names%20are%20aplenty%20in%20Kerala%2C%20pointing%20to%20its%20water%20wealth.%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20two%20main%20storylines%20that%20meet%20when%20this%20wealth%20turns%20into%20the%20scourge%20of%20Aruvikkulam.%20But%20the%20film%20salutes%20the%20selfless%20service%20of%20the%20fishermen%20community%2C%20who%20came%20forward%20with%20their%20boats%20and%20canoes%20to%20rescue%20over%2065%2C000%20people%20stranded%20in%20flood-wrecked%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAf3cjNPhM4o%3Fsi%3Dc2XBWc807tU1TcZj%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two-and-a-half%20hour%20film%20with%20an%20ensemble%20cast%20has%20Anoop%20(Tovino%20Thomas)%20in%20the%20lead%2C%20who%20has%20abandoned%20his%20military%20job%20out%20of%20fear%20for%20his%20life.%20Anoop%20is%20helping%20out%20the%20visually%20challenged%20Bhasi%20(Indrans)%20run%20his%20tea-shop%20while%20waiting%20for%20a%20Gulf%20visa%20and%20meets%20his%20fianc%C3%A9e%2C%20mistaking%20her%20first%20for%20an%20Army%20investigator%20out%20to%20expose%20his%20fake%20medical%20certificate.%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eshows%20the%20transformation%20of%20Anoop%20into%20a%20courageous%20jawan%2C%20saving%20lives%20and%20risking%20his%20own.%20Just%20like%20Nixon%20(Asif%20Ali)%2C%20who%20comes%20to%20value%20his%20roots%20by%20taking%20part%20in%20rescue%20efforts%20by%20fishermen%20who%20were%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstate%E2%80%99s%20own%20naval%20force%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20during%20the%20Kerala%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20has%20heartrending%20moments%20of%20people%20losing%20lives%20and%20hopes%20in%20the%20flood%20fury.%20Dreadful%20visuals%20of%20anguish%20and%20daredevilry%20are%20accompanied%20by%20an%20ominous%20soundtrack%2C%20making%20viewers%20relive%20the%20nightmare%3A%20an%20uprooted%20tree%20flowing%20down%20the%20raging%20waters%20and%20getting%20sucked%20up%20by%20an%20open%20dam%20shutter%3B%20a%20family%20with%20small%20children%20trapped%20in%20their%20house%20as%20a%20landslide%20engulfs%20it%20with%20slush%3B%20a%20couple%20holding%20onto%20the%20rooftop%20with%20their%20injured%2C%20autistic%20child%20as%20water%20lashes%20menacingly%20beneath%20them.%20Many%20an%20instance%20of%20resilience%20and%20compassion%20is%20captured%20and%20several%20of%20them%20are%20based%20on%20true%20events%3A%20like%20a%20north-Indian%20vendor%20donating%20all%20of%20his%20woolen%20blankets%20to%20a%20relief%20camp%3B%20the%20youth%20who%20volunteered%20in%20thousands%20to%20reach%20relief%20materials%20to%20camps%20and%20pass%20vital%20information%20on%20the%20stranded%3B%20a%20helicopter%20airlifting%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20third%20track%20is%20that%20of%20an%20arid%20Tamil%20Nadu%20village%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Mullaperiyar%20dam%2C%20a%20perennial%20spot%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20two%20states.%20In%20a%20poignant%20contrast%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enashicha%20mazha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(damned%20rain)%C2%A0on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20border%2C%20the%20village%20gleefully%20welcomes%20the%20showers.%20But%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20be%20more%20wide-ranging%2C%20the%20film%20has%20subplots%20of%20a%20couple%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20divorce%20and%20a%20foreign%20vlogger%20making%20merry%20amidst%20the%20ravage%20%E2%80%93%20serving%20only%20to%20lengthen%20its%20running%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20its%20name%20goes%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0makes%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eeveryone%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20hero.%20Even%20a%20lizard%20(which%20has%20a%20divine%20part%20to%20fulfil)%2C%20a%20fish%20and%20a%20cat%20get%20their%20due%20share%2C%20reminding%20viewers%20of%20the%20hapless%20dog%20and%20numerous%20other%20animals%20in%20legendary%20writer%20Thakazhi%E2%80%99s%20famed%20story%20%3Cem%3EVellappokkathil%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Deluge%E2%80%9D).%20The%20movie%20rightly%20acknowledges%20the%20role%20the%20media%20played%20in%20relaying%20not%20only%20chaos%20and%20tears%20but%20also%20solidarity%20and%20kindness%20%5Balthough%20how%20is%20the%20opening%20of%20Idukki%20dam%20shutters%20an%20exclusive%20story%20as%20claimed%20by%20channel%20head%20Noora%20(Aparna%20Balamurali)%20when%20she%20is%20seen%20reporting%20it%20with%20more%20than%20a%20few%20others%3F%5D.%20The%20control%20room%20official%20Shaji%20(Kunchacko%20Boban)%20echoes%20the%20thought%20of%20every%20Malayali%20during%20those%20days%3A%20%E2%80%9Crain%20used%20to%20refresh%20me%20once%3B%20now%20I%20just%20wish%20for%20it%20to%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0cannot%20be%20considered%20an%20authentic%20reflection%20of%20what%20transpired%20in%20Kerala%20in%20the%20month%20of%20August%202018%20when%20the%20state%20received%20821%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20as%20against%20419.3%20mm%20in%20normal%20course.%20The%20tragedy%20still%20raises%20pertinent%20questions%20about%20dam%20management%20and%20early%20warning%20systems%20but%20what%20shows%20up%20primarily%20is%20the%20way%20the%20state%20machinery%20rose%20to%20the%20challenge%20when%20flash%20floods%20struck.%20The%20remarkable%20way%20in%20which%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20representatives%2C%20transcending%20party%20affiliations%2C%20coordinated%20%C2%A0relief%20and%20rescue%20remains%20a%20lesson%20in%20democracy%20which%20the%20movie%20fails%20to%20highlight.%20Just%20as%20nothing%20more%20is%20said%20about%20the%20Kundala%20Valley%20hill%20railway%20swept%20away%20by%20the%20Periyar%20despite%20piquing%20viewers%E2%80%99%20curiosity.%20Even%20so%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E2018%3A%20Everyone%20is%20a%20Hero%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20skilful%20account%20of%20humanity%E2%80%99s%20triumph%20over%20a%20fateful%20night%20when%20rain%2C%20instead%20of%20delight%2C%20spelt%20devastation%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERasmi%20Binoy%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20author%20based%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Kerala.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696156217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01153204%2F2018-Ev