20almost%20every%20village%20of%20Kashmir.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20is%20like%20a%20religious%20duty%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F184821%2Fkashmir-guide-saves-tourist-drowning-rouf-ahmad-dar-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20will%20continue%20this%20mission%20till%20my%20last%20breath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20who%20still%20works%20as%20a%20daily%20wager%20to%20eke%20out%20his%20living%2C%20has%20dedicated%20two%20days%20a%20week%20to%20nurturing%20these%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20climate%20is%20very%20hot%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echinars%20%3C%2Fem%3Erequire%20to%20be%20watered%20periodically.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20work%20for%20two%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20I%20spend%20my%20entire%20day%20watering%20them.%20Though%20I%20am%20poor%20and%20work%20as%20a%20labourer%2C%20I%20nurture%20these%20trees%20like%20my%20own%20kids%3B%20they%20are%20like%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%20has%20not%20married%20and%20lives%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20brothers.%20He%20has%20inspired%20his%20family%20and%20others%20to%20look%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Khan%20has%20now%20extended%20his%20mission%20by%20planting%20%3Cem%3Edeodar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20other%20pine%20trees%20in%20the%20forests.%20He%20can%20expertly%20handle%20this%20task%20now%20after%20updating%20himself%20about%20it.%20He%20continues%20to%20work%20in%20plantation%20drives%20and%20hopes%20that%20others%20will%20recognise%20the%20need%20for%20immediate%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20many%20aren%E2%80%99t%20much%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20social%20work%20in%20my%20area%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20who%20visit%20and%20help%20me%20out.%20I%20hope%20someday%