0Our%20designs%20prioritise%20functionality%20and%20longevity%20with%20diverse%20silhouettes.%20Our%20collection%20highlights%20innovative%20upcycling%20techniques%20with%20simple%20shapes%20and%20functional%20details%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Gouri%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%20this%20brand%2C%20we%20had%20this%20idea%20of%20working%20around%20sustainability.%20Coming%20from%20a%20design%20background%2C%20my%20initial%20thoughts%20were%20to%20create%20pieces%20that%20are%20so%20eclectic%20in%20nature%20and%20well%20thought%20out%20that%20people%20would%20be%20shocked%20to%20find%20out%20products%20like%20these%20are%20made%20out%20of%20waste.%20This%20was%20the%20design%20philosophy%20that%20more%20or%20less%20went%20into%20our%20products.%20For%20example%2C%20Noir%20Et%20Blanc%20features%20a%20monochromatic%20approach%2C%20while%20Gold%20Riddance%20uses%20bold%20gold%20tones.%20We%20showcase%20craftsmanship%20in%20our%20High-Braid%20all-upcycled%20leather%20line.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20accessories%20need%20to%20be%20very%20utilitarian%20and%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20just%20part%20of%20another%20fad.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20create%20accessories%20that%20would%20eventually%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%20once%20a%20seasonal%20trend%20has%20passed.%20They%20are%20durable%20in%20terms%20of%20material%2C%20utilitarian%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20functionality%2C%20and%20design-wise%2C%20they%20are%20archival%20so%20that%20they%20remain%20in%20your%20wardrobe%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoving%20ahead%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20expanding%20their%20product%20range%20to%20include%20jewellery%20crafted%20from%20scrap%20leather%20and%20metal%2C%20and%20have%20developed%20a%20new%20fabric%20made%20from%20waste%20threads.%20Emblematic%20of%20their%20new%20product%20range%20is%20their%20upcoming%20collection%20%E2%80%98Creation%20of%20Eve%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20reimag